#: finbodh.tra:33
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Ahhh... my dear brother calls me at last, does he?  I knew you would not be "
#| "able to live without my assistance for long."
msgid ""
"Ahhh... my dear brother calls me at last, does he? I knew you would not be "
"able to live without my assistance for long."
msgstr ""
"Ah... mein lieber Bruder ruft mich schließlich doch.  Ich wusste, er würde "
"nicht lange ohne meine Hilfe leben können."

#: finbodh.tra:34
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "(chuckle)  How very like you to blame me for your own failings.  Poor, poor "
#| "Irenicus... always so very, very close to getting what he wants and yet "
#| "always so very, very far."
msgid ""
"(chuckle) How very like you to blame me for your own failings. Poor, poor "
"Irenicus... always so very, very close to getting what he wants and yet "
"always so very, very far."
msgstr ""
"(Kichert)  Wie typisch für Euch, mir die Schuld an Eurem eigenen Versagen zu"
" geben.  Armer, armer Irenicus... immer so kurz davor, das eigene Ziel zu "
"erreichen, und doch immer so weit davon entfernt."

#: finbodh.tra:35
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "So I see.  How absolutely delicious to let me in on your little play with "
#| "the Bhaalspawn again, brother dear.  And how are you, <CHARNAME>?  I do so "
#| "hope you are as... healthy... as I remember.  Shall we continue our merry "
#| "dance?"
msgid ""
"So I see. How absolutely delicious to let me in on your little play with the"
" Bhaalspawn again, brother dear. And how are you, <CHARNAME>? I do so hope "
"you are as... healthy... as I remember. Shall we continue our merry dance?"
msgstr ""
"Ah, ich sehe.  Wie überaus köstlich, dass Ihr mich wieder an Eurem kleinen "
"Spiel mit dem Bhaalkind beteiligt, liebster Bruder.  Und wie geht es Euch, "
"<CHARNAME>?  Ich hoffe, Ihr seid so... gesund... wie ich Euch in Erinnerung "
"habe. Sollen wir unseren fröhlichen Tanz fortführen?"

#: finbodh.tra:36
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Still trapped in servitude to Irenicus?  Do you have no will of your own, "
#| "Bodhi?"
msgid ""
"Still trapped in servitude to Irenicus? Do you have no will of your own, "
"Bodhi?"
msgstr ""
"Seid Ihr immer noch in gefangen in Knechtschaft zu Irenicus?  Habt Ihr denn "
"gar keinen eigenen Willen, Bodhi?"

#: finbodh.tra:37
msgid ""
"Why don't you go jump on a stake and spare us both the tedium of battle?"
msgstr ""
"Warum stürzt Ihr Euch nicht in einen Holzpflock und erspart uns beide die "
"Langeweile eines Kampfes?"

#: finbodh.tra:38
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Best hike up your skirts and run, Bodhi.  The time when I found vampires "
#| "remotely threatening is long past!"
msgid ""
"Best hike up your skirts and run, Bodhi. The time when I found vampires "
"remotely threatening is long past!"
msgstr ""
"Am besten rafft Ihr Euren Rock, Bodhi, und lauft davon.  Die Zeiten, wo ich "
"Vampire auch nur ein bisschen bedrohlich fand, sind längst vorbei."

#: finbodh.tra:39
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Do I have to suffer your prattle again?  I shall stamp out your evil "
#| "presence once and for all!"
msgid ""
"Do I have to suffer your prattle again? I shall stamp out your evil presence"
" once and for all!"
msgstr ""
"Muss ich Euer Geplapper erneut ertragen?  Ich sollte Eure bösartige "
"Erscheinung ausradieren... und zwar für immer!"

#: finbodh.tra:41
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Oh Child of Bhaal, so serious and grim!  Do you not enjoy that our paths "
#| "have crossed again?  Does your blood not rejoice?"
msgid ""
"Oh Child of Bhaal, so serious and grim! Do you not enjoy that our paths have"
" crossed again? Does your blood not rejoice?"
msgstr ""
"Oh Kind des Bhaal, so ernst und grimmig!  Freut Ihr Euch nicht, dass sich "
"unsere Wege ein weiteres Mal kreuzen?  Bringt es nicht Euer Blut in Wallung?"

#: finbodh.tra:42
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You are weak, Bodhi, while the blood of a god flows within me.  I shall "
#| "enjoy your death... again."
msgid ""
"You are weak, Bodhi, while the blood of a god flows within me. I shall enjoy"
" your death... again."
msgstr ""
"Ihr seid schwach, Bodhi, während in meinen Adern das Blut eines Gottes "
"fließt.  Euer Tod wird mich erfreuen... ein weiteres Mal."

#: finbodh.tra:43
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Enough of this!  You will fall before me, undead thing."
msgid "Enough of this! You will fall before me, undead thing."
msgstr "Genug davon!  Ihr werdet vor mir im Staub liegen, untotes Ding."

#: finbodh.tra:44
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You have nothing to gain from this fight.  Will you sacrifice yourself out "
#| "of sibling loyalty?  Do not make that mistake again."
msgid ""
"You have nothing to gain from this fight. Will you sacrifice yourself out of"
" sibling loyalty? Do not make that mistake again."
msgstr ""
"Ihr habt nichts zu gewinnen in diesem Kampf.  Wollt Ihr Euch wirklich opfern"
" aus Loyalität zu Eurem Bruder?  Macht den gleichen Fehler nicht ein zweites"
" Mal."

#: finbodh.tra:45
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Stand aside Bodhi.  Your brother is blinded by his lust for vengance.  He's "
#| "prepared to fight me to the death, but you don't need to die at his side.  "
#| "There is no need for you to die at all."
msgid ""
"Stand aside Bodhi. Your brother is blinded by his lust for vengance. He's "
"prepared to fight me to the death, but you don't need to die at his side. "
"There is no need for you to die at all."
msgstr ""
"Tretet zur Seite Bodhi.  Euer Bruder ist geblendet von seiner Lust auf "
"Rache.  Er ist gewillt, mich bis in den Tod hinein zu bekämpfen, aber Ihr "
"müsst nicht an seiner Seite sterben. Ihr müsst überhaupt nicht sterben."

#: finbodh.tra:46
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You may be strong, <CHARNAME>, but you are indeed a fool to think us weak.  "
#| "I shall take your soul for my own, I swear it!"
msgid ""
"You may be strong, <CHARNAME>, but you are indeed a fool to think us weak. I"
" shall take your soul for my own, I swear it!"
msgstr ""
"Ihr mögt stark sein, <CHARNAME>, aber Ihr seid auch ein Narr, wenn Ihr uns "
"für schwach haltet.  Ich werde Eure Seele für mich selbst behalten, ich "
"schwöre es!"

#: finbodh.tra:47
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You had your chance, brother.  Your plans failed, as I recall, and brought "
#| "about my death.  No, you are weak and <CHARNAME> is strong and it is "
#| "<PRO_HESHE> that shall give me what I need.  I look forward to bathing in "
#| "your blood, dear brother... a suitable reward for your utter failure."
msgid ""
"You had your chance, brother. Your plans failed, as I recall, and brought "
"about my death. No, you are weak and <CHARNAME> is strong and it is "
"<PRO_HESHE> that shall give me what I need. I look forward to bathing in "
"your blood, dear brother... a suitable reward for your utter failure."
msgstr ""
"Ihr hattet Eure Chance, Bruder.  Eure Pläne versagten, wenn ich Euch daran "
"erinnern darf, und brachten mir den Tod.  Nun seid Ihr schwach und "
"<CHARNAME> ist stark und es ist <PRO_HESHE>, der mir geben kann, was ich "
"brauche.  Ich kann es nicht abwarten, in Eurem Blut zu baden, mein lieber "
"Bruder... das ist die Quittung für Euer komplettes Versagen."

#: finbodh.tra:48
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Oh Child of Bhaal, you do bore me so with your talk.  Come to me and embrace"
#| " death as I have.  Let the dance begin again!"
msgid ""
"Oh Child of Bhaal, you do bore me so with your talk. Come to me and embrace "
"death as I have. Let the dance begin again!"
msgstr ""
"Oh Kind des Bhaal, Ihr langweilt mich mit Eurem Gerede.  Kommt zu mir und "
"umarmt den Tod wie ich es tat.  Lasst den Tanz erneut beginnen!"

#: finbodh.tra:49
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Indeed, I have no intention of dying at all.   I fight with my brother "
#| "because I have no choice....or would you offer me one now?"
msgid ""
"Indeed, I have no intention of dying at all. I fight with my brother because"
" I have no choice....or would you offer me one now?"
msgstr ""
"Wahrhaftig, ich habe keinerlei Absicht zu sterben.  Ich kämpfe mit meinem "
"Bruder, weil ich keine Wahl habe... oder bietet Ihr mir eine?"

#: finbodh.tra:50
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "My brother believes he can offer me your soul, yet I see that you too can "
#| "raise others from the abyss; one who opposed you, no less!  How intriguing."
#| "  Perhaps I do not need to taste your blood..."
msgid ""
"My brother believes he can offer me your soul, yet I see that you too can "
"raise others from the abyss, one who opposed you, no less! How intriguing. "
"Perhaps I do not need to taste your blood..."
msgstr ""
"Mein Bruder glaubt, er könne mir Eure Seele anbieten.  Jetzt aber sehe ich, "
"dass auch Ihr andere aus der Abyss zurückrufen könnt... sogar welche, die "
"Euch bekämpft haben!  Wie faszinierend!  Vielleicht brauche ich nicht Euer "
"Blut trinken..."

#: finbodh.tra:51
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I would make you an offer <CHARNAME>.  Promise me a piece of your soul and I"
#| " shall fight as a sister to you."
msgid ""
"I would make you an offer <CHARNAME>. Promise me a piece of your soul and I "
"shall fight as a sister to you."
msgstr ""
"Ich mache Euch ein Angebot <CHARNAME>.  Versprecht mir einen Teil Eurer "
"Seele und ich werde als Eure Schwester mit Euch kämpfen."

#: finbodh.tra:52
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I require a soul <CHARNAME>, as well you know.  I could tear it from young "
#| "Imoen once again, but she seems....indisposed.  Yet perhaps there is another"
#| " way..."
msgid ""
"I require a soul <CHARNAME>, as well you know. I could tear it from young "
"Imoen once again, but she seems....indisposed. Yet perhaps there is another "
"way..."
msgstr ""
"Ich brauche eine Seele <CHARNAME>, wie ihr sicherlich sehr gut wisst.  Ich "
"könnte sie wieder der kleinen Imoen entreißen, aber sie scheint... "
"unpässlich zu sein. Aber vielleicht gibt es ja einen anderen Weg..."

#: finbodh.tra:53
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I am doomed whether or not I fight.  My stay in the Abyss was not a pleasant"
#| " one, but since I must return, I shall not pass up a chance to feast on such"
#| " a fine morsel."
msgid ""
"I am doomed whether or not I fight. My stay in the Abyss was not a pleasant "
"one, but since I must return, I shall not pass up a chance to feast on such "
"a fine morsel."
msgstr ""
"Ich bin verdammt, ob ich nun kämpfe oder nicht.  Mein Aufenthalt in der "
"Abyss war kein angenehmer, aber da ich dorthin zurückkehren muss, werde ich "
"die Gelegenheit, mich an einem so leckeren Happen gütlich zu tun, nicht "
"verstreichen lassen."

#: finbodh.tra:54
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I have power beyond your brother's.  Join with me and I shall grant the "
#| "reward he shall not live to bestow; a soul."
msgid ""
"I have power beyond your brother's. Join with me and I shall grant the "
"reward he shall not live to bestow, a soul."
msgstr ""
"Ich habe Kräfte, weit mächtiger als die Eures Bruders.  Kämpft mit mir und "
"ich werde Euch ein Geschenk überreichen, welches er Euch wird niemals geben "
"können: Eine Seele."

#: finbodh.tra:55
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I have changed since our last encounter, Bodhi.  I am above you and your "
#| "pitiful games.  They bore me and I shall put an end to them!"
msgid ""
"I have changed since our last encounter, Bodhi. I am above you and your "
"pitiful games. They bore me and I shall put an end to them!"
msgstr ""
"Ich habe mich verändert, Bodhi, seid wir uns das letzte Mal trafen.  Ich "
"stehe weit über Euch und Euren jämmerlichen Spielchen.  Sie langweiligen "
"mich und ich werde ihnen ein Ende setzen."

#: finbodh.tra:56
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "So much talk from your brother, Bodhi, yet actions speak louder than words."
#| "  How many deaths has your brother granted me?  Do you truly believe you can"
#| " win?  Take the portion of soul I offer and live again."
msgid ""
"So much talk from your brother, Bodhi, yet actions speak louder than words. "
"How many deaths has your brother granted me? Do you truly believe you can "
"win? Take the portion of soul I offer and live again."
msgstr ""
"So viel Gerede von Eurem Bruder, Bodhi, aber Taten sprechen lauter als "
"Worte.  Wie viele Tode hat er mir bereits geschworen? Glaubt Ihr wirklich zu"
" gewinnen?  Nehmt das bisschen  Seele, das ich Euch anbiete, und lebt "
"wieder."

#: finbodh.tra:57
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Such a delicious offer you make... though I must wonder if you are telling "
#| "the truth.  Are my chances of survival really any better with you...?"
msgid ""
"Such a delicious offer you make... though I must wonder if you are telling "
"the truth. Are my chances of survival really any better with you...?"
msgstr ""
"Ein verführerisches Angebot macht Ihr mir... aber ich frage mich, ob Ihr die"
" Wahrheit sprecht.  Sind meine Chancen zu überleben wirklich besser mit "
"Euch...?"

#: finbodh.tra:58
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "So <CHARNAME>, the creature of darkness that rests within you has also "
#| "stolen your wit.  Such a shame for one with the divine essence.  It will "
#| "almost be a mercy to end your existence."
msgid ""
"So <CHARNAME>, the creature of darkness that rests within you has also "
"stolen your wit. Such a shame for one with the divine essence. It will "
"almost be a mercy to end your existence."
msgstr ""
"Also <CHARNAME>, hat die Kreatur der Dunkelheit, die in Euch ruht, auch "
"Euren Verstand gestohlen.  Welch eine Schande für Jemanden mit göttlicher "
"Essenz.  Es wird eine Wohltat sein, Eure Existenz zu beenden."

#: finbodh.tra:59
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "An opportunity to feast on the blood of a God, and yet you think I will "
#| "stand aside?  (chuckle)  You know me no better than my dear brother here."
msgid ""
"An opportunity to feast on the blood of a God, and yet you think I will "
"stand aside? (chuckle) You know me no better than my dear brother here."
msgstr ""
"Eine Möglichkeit, mich am Blute eines Gottes zu laben, und Ihr glaubt, ich "
"würde beiseite treten?  (kichert)  Ihr kennt mich kein Stück besser als mein"
" lieber Bruder hier."

#: finbodh.tra:60
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Nor would I care to.  Soon enough you will return to the torment you "
#| "deserve."
msgid ""
"Nor would I care to. Soon enough you will return to the torment you deserve."
msgstr ""
"Und es interessiert mich auch nicht. Bald schon werdet Ihr dorthin zurück "
"kehren, wo Ihr hingehört."

#: finbodh.tra:61
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Well, well, well... if the Child of Bhaal hasn't gone and found "
#| "<PRO_HIMHER>self a sense of humour.  Did <PRO_HESHE> dig it up all by "
#| "<PRO_HIMHER>self, dear brother, or did you implant it in <PRO_HIMHER> in one"
#| " of your more bizarre experiments?"
msgid ""
"Well, well, well... if the Child of Bhaal hasn't gone and found "
"<PRO_HIMHER>self a sense of humour. Did <PRO_HESHE> dig it up all by "
"<PRO_HIMHER>self, dear brother, or did you implant it in <PRO_HIMHER> in one"
" of your more bizarre experiments?"
msgstr ""
"Soso... da hat das Bhaalkind doch tatsächlich ein bisschen Sinn für Humor "
"entwickelt. Tat <PRO_HESHE> das ganz alleine, lieber Bruder, oder habt Ihr "
"es <PRO_HIMHER> in einem Eurer bizarren Experimente implantiert?"

#: finbodh.tra:62
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I see you are now more Slayer than <PRO_MANWOMAN>.  How dull.  You provided "
#| "such small amusement last time, I doubt that this will be different."
msgid ""
"I see you are now more Slayer than <PRO_MANWOMAN>. How dull. You provided "
"such small amusement last time, I doubt that this will be different."
msgstr ""
"Ich sehe, Ihr seid mehr Schlächter als <PRO_MANWOMAN>.  Wie langweilig.  Ihr"
" botet wenig Unterhaltung beim letzten Mal, ich bezweifle, dass es diesmal "
"anders sein würde."

#: finbodh.tra:63
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "No, <CHARNAME>.  Sadly, I do not think we are destined to work together "
#| "again.  I am content to fight by my brother and revel in your blood and that"
#| " of those that follow at your heel."
msgid ""
"No, <CHARNAME>. Sadly, I do not think we are destined to work together "
"again. I am content to fight by my brother and revel in your blood and that "
"of those that follow at your heel."
msgstr ""
"Nein, <CHARNAME>. Leider glaube ich nicht, dass wir dafür bestimmt sind, "
"erneut zusammenzuarbeiten.  Ich bin bereit, zusammen mit meinem Bruder zu "
"kämpfen und ich werde schwelgen in Eurem Blut und in dem derer, die Euch "
"gefolgt sind."

#: finbodh.tra:64
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Oh Child of Bhaal, such a game you play.  You think to trick me, but I shall"
#| " not be fooled so easily.  I know you to be ever so desperate to do 'good' "
#| "and this would not bode well for me.  No, this ends here."
msgid ""
"Oh Child of Bhaal, such a game you play. You think to trick me, but I shall "
"not be fooled so easily. I know you to be ever so desperate to do 'good' and"
" this would not bode well for me. No, this ends here."
msgstr ""
"Oh Kind des Bhaal, welches Spiel treibt Ihr mit mir.  Ihr glaubt mich "
"betrügen zu können, aber so leicht ist das nicht.  Ihr ward immer so "
"verzweifelt bemüht 'Gutes' zu tun und dieses lässt mich nichts 'Gutes' "
"erwarten.  Nein, hier endet es."

#: finbodh.tra:65
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Oh Child of Bhaal, such a game you play.  I fight with my 'dear' brother for"
#| " your soul, yet you would offer it willingly?  Promise me a piece of your "
#| "essence and I will join you... for now."
msgid ""
"Oh Child of Bhaal, such a game you play. I fight with my 'dear' brother for "
"your soul, yet you would offer it willingly? Promise me a piece of your "
"essence and I will join you... for now."
msgstr ""
"Oh Kind des Bhaal, welches Spiel treibt Ihr mit mir.  Ich kämpfe zusammen "
"mit meinem Bruder wegen Eurer Seele, und nun bietet Ihr sie freiwillig an?  "
"Versprecht mir einen Teil Eurer Essenz und ich werde für Euch kämpfen... "
"zumindest vorläufig."

#: finbodh.tra:66
msgid ""
"I swear to you Bodhi, fight by my side, kill my enemies, and you shall have "
"the soul you desire."
msgstr ""
"Ich schwöre es Euch Bodhi, kämpft an meiner Seite, tötet meine Feinde, und "
"Ihr sollt die Seele erhalten, die Ihr so sehr wünscht."

#: finbodh.tra:67
msgid ""
"You have my word Bodhi that when this is done, you shall have a piece of my "
"essence."
msgstr ""
"Ihr habt mein Wort, Bodhi, dass, wenn dieses abgeschlossen ist, Ihr einen "
"Teil meiner Essenz erhalten werdet."

#: finbodh.tra:68
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Actually Bodhi, I have changed my mind.  I enjoy watching you die too much, "
#| "to pass up an opportunity to see it again."
msgid ""
"Actually Bodhi, I have changed my mind. I enjoy watching you die too much, "
"to pass up an opportunity to see it again."
msgstr ""
"Nun Bodhi, ich habe meine Meinung geändert.  Ich liebe es zu sehr, Euch "
"sterben zu sehen, als dass ich eine solche Gelegenheit verpassen wollte."

#: finbodh.tra:69
msgid "Bodhi, when this is over, I swear that you will be fittingly rewarded."
msgstr ""
"Bodhi, wenn dieses alles vorüber ist, dann werdet Ihr eine angemessene "
"Belohnung erhalten. Dieses schwöre ich Euch."

#: finbodh.tra:70
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Pray that you hold to your word, failure to do so would be... unpleasant for"
#| " you.  Now to finalize matters..."
msgid ""
"Pray that you hold to your word, failure to do so would be... unpleasant for"
" you. Now to finalize matters..."
msgstr ""
"Betet, dass Ihr Euer Wort haltet, es nicht zu tun, würde... unangenehm für "
"Euch werden. Und nun lasst uns zum Abschluss kommen... "

#: finbodh.tra:71
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "No, <CHARNAME>.  Sadly, I do not think we are destined to work together "
#| "again.  Despite the attractiveness of what you offer, your words ring more "
#| "hollow than my brother's.  Far better to rip your soul from your living "
#| "breast than beg for it at your side."
msgid ""
"No, <CHARNAME>. Sadly, I do not think we are destined to work together "
"again. Despite the attractiveness of what you offer, your words ring more "
"hollow than my brother's. Far better to rip your soul from your living "
"breast than beg for it at your side."
msgstr ""
"Nein, <CHARNAME>. Leider glaube ich nicht, dass es uns bestimmt ist, wieder "
"zusammenzuarbeiten.  Obwohl Euer Angebot verführerisch ist, so klingen Eure "
"Worte doch hohl und leer. Nein, es ist besser, Eure Seele aus Eurem lebenden"
" Körper zu reißen als an Eurer Seite darum zu betteln."

#: finbodh.tra:72
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I require satisfaction before the Child of Bhaal makes any sort of decision,"
#| " creature.  Both my brother and this... Melissan, lie dead.  Your hunt has "
#| "been delightfully successful, <CHARNAME>."
msgid ""
"I require satisfaction before the Child of Bhaal makes any sort of decision,"
" creature. Both my brother and this... Melissan, lie dead. Your hunt has "
"been delightfully successful, <CHARNAME>."
msgstr ""
"Ich verlange meine Belohnung, bevor das Bhaalkind irgendeine Entscheidung "
"trifft, Kreatur.  Sowohl mein Bruder als auch diese... Melissan sind tot.  "
"Eure Jagd war sehr erfolgreich, <CHARNAME>."

#: finbodh.tra:73
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "But do not forget our deal.  I am impatient for the piece of your soul you "
#| "promised me.  I have enjoyed our dance Child of Bhaal, but I tire of this "
#| "place.  Give me what I want so I may leave... we need not meet each other "
#| "again, unless you wish it."
msgid ""
"But do not forget our deal. I am impatient for the piece of your soul you "
"promised me. I have enjoyed our dance Child of Bhaal, but I tire of this "
"place. Give me what I want so I may leave... we need not meet each other "
"again, unless you wish it."
msgstr ""
"Aber vergesst nicht unsere Abmachung.  Ich will unbedingt den Teil Eurer "
"Seele haben, den Ihr mir versprochen habt.  Unser Tanz hat mir gefallen, "
"Kind von Bhaal, aber dieser Ort langweilt mich.  Gebt mir, was ich will, und"
" ich werde gehen... Wir brauchen uns nicht wieder zu sehen, außer Ihr "
"wünscht es."

#: finbodh.tra:74
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "It was a pleasure to have you fight by my side, Bodhi.  You have earned this"
#| " reward."
msgid ""
"It was a pleasure to have you fight by my side, Bodhi. You have earned this "
"reward."
msgstr ""
"Es war ein Vergnügen, Euch an meiner Seite zu sehen, Bodhi.  Ihr habt Euch "
"Eure Belohnung verdient."

#: finbodh.tra:75
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You shall have nothing.  Your use to me is at an end.  I shall enjoy sending"
#| " you screaming back into the abyss."
msgid ""
"You shall have nothing. Your use to me is at an end. I shall enjoy sending "
"you screaming back into the abyss."
msgstr ""
"Ihr sollt nichts haben.  Eure Nützlichkeit für mich hat sich erschöpft.  Ich"
" werde es genießen, Euch keifend zurück in die Abyss zu schicken."

#: finbodh.tra:76
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Hmmm, I could kill you... no, I have better things to do.  Take these scraps"
#| " of my essence and depart."
msgid ""
"Hmmm, I could kill you... no, I have better things to do. Take these scraps "
"of my essence and depart."
msgstr ""
"Hmmm, ich könnte Euch töten... aber nein, ich habe besseres zu tun.  Nehmt "
"diesen Teil meiner Essenz und verschwindet."

#: finbodh.tra:77
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "No Bodhi, I think I will keep all of my soul.  You will fall back into the "
#| "abyss.  Give Bhaal my regards."
msgid ""
"No Bodhi, I think I will keep all of my soul. You will fall back into the "
"abyss. Give Bhaal my regards."
msgstr ""
"Nein Bodhi, ich gedenke, jeden Teil meiner Seele zu behalten.  Ihr werdet in"
" die Abyss zurückfallen.  Bestellt Bhaal meine Grüße."

#: finbodh.tra:78
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Fool!  You think to betray me, Child of Bhaal?  I refuse to return to the "
#| "abyss.  I shall rip every shred of that soul from your body!  Let the dance "
#| "end here!"
msgid ""
"Fool! You think to betray me, Child of Bhaal? I refuse to return to the "
"abyss. I shall rip every shred of that soul from your body! Let the dance "
"end here!"
msgstr ""
"Narr!  Ihr glaubt mich betrügen zu können, Kind von Bhaal?  Niemals kehre "
"ich in die Abyss zurück.  Stattdessen werde ich jeden Fetzen Seele aus Eurem"
" Körper reißen!  Lasst den Tanz hier enden!"

#: finbodh.tra:79
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "This is my realm, Bodhi.  I control everything here.  It is time for you to "
#| "join your brother."
msgid ""
"This is my realm, Bodhi. I control everything here. It is time for you to "
"join your brother."
msgstr ""
"Hier ist mein Reich, Bodhi.  Hier regiere ich.  Es wird Zeit, Eurem Bruder "
"zu folgen."

#: finbodh.tra:80
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Enough talk!  The dance has come to an end, Bodhi, and so has your part in "
#| "it."
msgid ""
"Enough talk! The dance has come to an end, Bodhi, and so has your part in "
"it."
msgstr ""
"Genug geredet!  Der Tanz ist zum Ende gekommen, Bodhi, und gleiches gilt für"
" Euren Anteil daran."

#: finbodh.tra:81
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Die!  Witness my power, insect!"
msgid "Die! Witness my power, insect!"
msgstr "Sterbt!  Spürt meine Macht, Insekt!"

#: finbodh.tra:82
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Oh Bodhi, you should have begged.  I would have liked to see that.  Too late"
#| " now."
msgid ""
"Oh Bodhi, you should have begged. I would have liked to see that. Too late "
"now."
msgstr ""
"Oh Bodhi, Ihr hättet darum betteln sollen.  Wie gerne hätte ich das gesehen."
"  Nun aber ist es zu spät."

#: finbodh.tra:83
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "So you have betrayed me, <CHARNAME>.  It would seem that working together "
#| "was never our true calling."
msgid ""
"So you have betrayed me, <CHARNAME>. It would seem that working together was"
" never our true calling."
msgstr ""
"So habt Ihr mich betrogen, <CHARNAME>.  Es scheint, dass Zusammenarbeit "
"niemals unsere Bestimmung war."

#: finbodh.tra:84
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Ahhhhh, such feeling.  I feel the life flow through me!  Such a gift you "
#| "carry Child of Bhaal...  such power...  such strength.  Oh this is simply "
#| "divine!"
msgid ""
"Ahhhhh, such feeling. I feel the life flow through me! Such a gift you carry"
" Child of Bhaal... such power... such strength. Oh this is simply divine!"
msgstr ""
"Ahhhhh, welch ein Gefühl.  Ich fühle das Leben durch meinen Körper strömen."
"  Welche Gaben Ihr in Euch tragt, Kind von Bhaal... welche Macht... welche "
"Stärke.  Oh, es ist einfach göttlich!"

#: finbodh.tra:85
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Such an ungrateful <PRO_MANWOMAN> you are.  Still, I have life once more, "
#| "and I intend to enjoy it.  Perhaps the wizards of Spellhold still wish to "
#| "play?"
msgid ""
"Such an ungrateful <PRO_MANWOMAN> you are. Still, I have life once more, and"
" I intend to enjoy it. Perhaps the wizards of Spellhold still wish to play?"
msgstr ""
"Welch undankbare Person Ihr seid.  Trotzdem... ich habe mein Leben zurück, "
"und ich habe die Absicht, es zu genießen.  Vielleicht möchten die Magier in "
"der Zauberfeste ein wenig spielen?"

#: finbodh.tra:86
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Well, Child of Bhaal, it would seem that our time together is at an end.  I "
#| "shall enjoy carrying this piece of you with me.  Perhaps we shall meet "
#| "again, you and I..."
msgid ""
"Well, Child of Bhaal, it would seem that our time together is at an end. I "
"shall enjoy carrying this piece of you with me. Perhaps we shall meet again,"
" you and I..."
msgstr ""
"Nun, Kind von Bhaal, es scheint, dass unsere gemeinsame Zeit jetzt endet.  "
"Ich werde es genießen, einen Teil von Euch in mir zu tragen.  Vielleicht "
"treffen wir uns eines Tages wieder, Ihr und ich..."

#: finbodh.tra:87
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Now, now, <CHARNAME>...there is no need to look at me so.  A tiny piece of "
#| "your soul would give me all I require and more.  Decide quickly, for I doubt"
#| " my dear brother will be content with merely withering me with his own "
#| "delightfully evil glare."
msgid ""
"Now, now, <CHARNAME>...there is no need to look at me so. A tiny piece of "
"your soul would give me all I require and more. Decide quickly, for I doubt "
"my dear brother will be content with merely withering me with his own "
"delightfully evil glare."
msgstr ""
"Nun, <CHARNAME>, starrt mich doch nicht so an.  Ein kleiner Teil Eurer Seele"
" ist alles, was ich benötige.  Aber entscheidet Euch schnell, denn ich "
"bezweifle, dass mein lieber Bruder seine Angriffe weiterhin auf herrlich "
"bösartige Blicke beschränken wird."

#: finbodh.tra:88
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Why you assumed I would even be interested in your allegiance, Bodhi, I have"
#| " no idea.  I shall be pleased to know that you both die again just as you "
#| "lived: without a single redeeming or worthwhile quality."
msgid ""
"Why you assumed I would even be interested in your allegiance, Bodhi, I have"
" no idea. I shall be pleased to know that you both die again just as you "
"lived: without a single redeeming or worthwhile quality."
msgstr ""
"Wieso glaubt Ihr, ich hätte irgendein Interesse an Eurer Unterstützung, "
"Bodhi?  Ich wäre hoch erfreut, wenn Ihr beide erneut sterben würdet so wie "
"Ihr gelebt habt: ohne Hoffnung und von allen verachtet."

#: finbodh.tra:89
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Pray that you hold to your word, failure to do so would be... unpleasant for"
#| " you.  Now to finalize matters...."
msgid ""
"Pray that you hold to your word, failure to do so would be... unpleasant for"
" you. Now to finalize matters...."
msgstr ""
"Betet, dass Ihr Euer Wort haltet, es nicht zu tun, würde... unangenehm für "
"Euch werden. Und nun lasst uns zum Abschluss kommen..."

#: finbodh.tra:90
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "No, <CHARNAME>.  Despite the attractiveness of what you offer, your words "
#| "ring more hollow than my brother's.  Far better to rip your soul from your "
#| "living breast than beg for it at your side."
msgid ""
"No, <CHARNAME>. Despite the attractiveness of what you offer, your words "
"ring more hollow than my brother's. Far better to rip your soul from your "
"living breast than beg for it at your side."
msgstr ""
"Nein, <CHARNAME>.  Obwohl Euer Angebot verführerisch ist, so klingen Eure "
"Worte doch hohl und leer. Nein, es ist besser, Eure Seele aus Eurem lebenden"
" Körper zu reißen als an Eurer Seite darum zu betteln."

#: finbodh.tra:91
msgid ""
"Goodbye, brother. Your self-destructive ways have cost you dearly. You were "
"a fool to oppose such power and I will not suffer in the abyss with you this"
" time."
msgstr ""

#: finbodh.tra:92
msgid ""
"It would seem our prey intends to cower inside the magics of this place, "
"<CHARNAME>. I have no patience for her games. I will have my soul!"
msgstr ""

#: finbodh.tra:93
msgid ""
"These pools around us have the stench of magic, if we sever their connection"
" to Melissan she will be forced to confront us. This is the realm of all "
"bhaalspawn, <CHARNAME>, your blood will serve you well."
msgstr ""

#: finmel01.tra:591
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You don't have all the essence of Bhaal... not by far.  And I rule here, as "
#| "well... you know that."
msgid ""
"You don't have all the essence of Bhaal... not by far. And I rule here, as "
"well... you know that."
msgstr ""
"Ihr besitzt nicht die gesamte Essenz des Bhaal... und Ihr regiert hier nicht"
" allein."

#: finmel01.tra:592
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You should have remained true to Bhaal, Melissan.  Only he could have saved "
#| "you now."
msgid ""
"You should have remained true to Bhaal, Melissan. Only he could have saved "
"you now."
msgstr ""
"Ihr hättet treu zu Bhaal stehen sollen... nur er könnte Euch jetzt retten!"

#: finmel01.tra:594
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Yeah, well, I suppose everyone has a dream.  Psycho."
msgid "Yeah, well, I suppose everyone has a dream. Psycho."
msgstr "Ja klar, jeder hat so seinen Traum, Wahnsinnige."

#: finmel01.tra:597
#, fuzzy
#| msgctxt "FINMEL25"
#| msgid ""
#| "Bah!  I should not be wasting time on you.  I still have to absorb the "
#| "Bhaalspawn essences... and there is more than enough power in this plane to "
#| "keep you busy.  Irenicus... Imoen... show <CHARNAME> the power <PRO_HESHE> "
#| "dares to oppose while I take what is mine!"
msgctxt "FINMEL25"
msgid ""
"Bah! I should not be wasting time on you. I still have to absorb the "
"Bhaalspawn essences... and there is more than enough power in this plane to "
"keep you busy. Irenicus... Imoen... show <CHARNAME> the power <PRO_HESHE> "
"dares to oppose while I take what is mine!"
msgstr ""
"Pah!  Ich sollte meine Zeit nicht mit Euch verschwenden!  Ich muss immer "
"noch die Essenzen der Bhaalbrut in mich aufnehmen... und es ist genug Macht "
"in dieser Ebene, um Euch zu beschäftigen.  Irenicus... Imoen... zeigt "
"<CHARNAME> die Macht, der <PRO_HESHE> es wagt entgegenzutreten, während ich "
"mir nehme, was mir gehört."

#: finmel01.tra:604
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You do not believe in my power, I can see that much.  You have fought "
#| "terrible foes in your past and have always managed to succeed.  Why... you "
#| "leave a trail of felled opponents littered about even here in the Abyss.  "
#| "Such as this one I found, discarded..."
msgid ""
"You do not believe in my power, I can see that much. You have fought "
"terrible foes in your past and have always managed to succeed. Why... you "
"leave a trail of felled opponents littered about even here in the Abyss. "
"Such as this one I found, discarded..."
msgstr ""
"Ihr glaubt nicht an meine Macht, ich kann es spüren.  Ihr habt in Eurer "
"Vergangenheit gegen mächtige Gegner gekämpft und immer habt ihr es geschafft"
" zu siegen.  Nun... Ihr hinterlasst eine Spur gefallener Feinde, sogar hier "
"in der Abyss. So fand ich zum Beispiel diesen hier..."

#: finmel01.tra:605
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "True.  More insightful than I would have expected from you, <CHARNAME>.  And"
#| " far more clever for you to have denied me Balthazar's essence... although, "
#| "to tell the truth, I was secretly hoping for him to have defeated you.  "
#| "Unlikely as that was, considering the pathetic monk could barely see the "
#| "forest for the trees."
msgid ""
"True. More insightful than I would have expected from you, <CHARNAME>. And "
"far more clever for you to have denied me Balthazar's essence... although, "
"to tell the truth, I was secretly hoping for him to have defeated you. "
"Unlikely as that was, considering the pathetic monk could barely see the "
"forest for the trees."
msgstr ""
"Ja, Ihr seit intelligenter als ich erwartet hatte, <CHARNAME>.  Und noch "
"intelligenter war es, mir Balthasars Essenz zu verweigern... obwohl, um "
"ehrlich zu sein, ich hatte insgeheim gehofft, er würde Euch besiegen können."
"  Unwahrscheinlich natürlich, wenn man bedenkt, dass der armselige Mönch "
"kaum den Wald vor lauter Bäumen sieht."

#: finmel01.tra:606
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I am disappointed in you, <CHARNAME>.  So much bluster, so much force.  So "
#| "much power and wisdom locked into such a fragile form.  I suppose you "
#| "actually believe you have a hope in opposing me, in seizing the Throne for "
#| "yourself.  Such delusions."
msgid ""
"I am disappointed in you, <CHARNAME>. So much bluster, so much force. So "
"much power and wisdom locked into such a fragile form. I suppose you "
"actually believe you have a hope in opposing me, in seizing the Throne for "
"yourself. Such delusions."
msgstr ""
"Ich bin enttäuscht von Euch, <CHARNAME>.  Soviel Energie, soviel Kraft.  "
"Soviel Macht und Weisheit eingesperrt in solch eine zerbrechliche Form.  Ich"
" nehme an, Ihr glaubt tatsächlich, dass Ihr eine Chance habt, mir zu "
"widerstehen und den Thron für Euch zu beanspruchen.  Welch eine Verblendung."

#: finmel01.tra:607
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Irenicus, I believe you called him.  So easily culled as my own, since you "
#| "abandoned him here recently... and such a valuable source of information on "
#| "you, <CHARNAME>.  After all... I believe you did share a soul, once, no?  "
#| "Say hello to the dear <PRO_MANWOMAN>, Irenicus."
msgid ""
"Irenicus, I believe you called him. So easily culled as my own, since you "
"abandoned him here recently... and such a valuable source of information on "
"you, <CHARNAME>. After all... I believe you did share a soul, once, no? Say "
"hello to the dear <PRO_MANWOMAN>, Irenicus."
msgstr ""
"Irenicus, so habt Ihr ihn wohl genannt.  So einfach war es, ihn zu finden, "
"da Ihr ihn ja erst kürzlich hier zurückgelassen habt... und was für eine "
"wertvolle Informationsquelle er war, <CHARNAME>.  Ich glaube, ihr hattet "
"einst eine gemeinsame Seele, oder nicht? Irenicus, sagt Hallo zu dem jungen "
"Herrn. "

#: finmel01.tra:608
msgid ""
"Of course, if you truly desire a demonstration of my influence over the "
"essence, that can be provided as well."
msgstr ""
"Nun, wenn Ihr wirklich eine Demonstration meiner Macht über die Essenzen "
"wünscht, so kann ich dieses gerne tun."

#: finmel01.tra:609
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Come, Imoen.  I command the essence within you.  You are not ready to be "
#| "here... and yet here you are.  Let's see just how much of my power is "
#| "contained in your young little soul, hmm?"
msgid ""
"Come, Imoen. I command the essence within you. You are not ready to be "
"here... and yet here you are. Let's see just how much of my power is "
"contained in your young little soul, hmm?"
msgstr ""
"Los, Imoen.  Ich kontrolliere die Essenz in Euch.  Ihr seit noch nicht "
"fertig, hier zu sein... und jetzt seit Ihr hier.  Lasst uns doch einmal "
"sehen, wie viel Macht in Eurer kleinen, jungen Seele steckt, hmmm?"

#: finmel01.tra:610
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "It seems you've misplaced your darling little Imoen, haven't you?  But her "
#| "essence is easy enough to command.  Let's see what she has to say, shall we?"
msgid ""
"It seems you've misplaced your darling little Imoen, haven't you? But her "
"essence is easy enough to command. Let's see what she has to say, shall we?"
msgstr ""
"Es scheint so, als ob Euch die kleine Imoen verloren gegangen ist, oder?  "
"Aber ihre Essenz ist leicht zu kontrollieren.  Wollen doch mal hören, was "
"sie zu sagen hat, nicht wahr?"

#: finmel01.tra:611
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You don't have to go anywhere, little one.  I'm not calling you, after "
#| "all... I'm merely coaxing forth your essence."
msgid ""
"You don't have to go anywhere, little one. I'm not calling you, after all..."
" I'm merely coaxing forth your essence."
msgstr ""
"Ihr müsst nirgendwo hingehen, meine Kleine.  Ich rufe nicht Euch, sondern "
"ich rufe lediglich Eure Essenz hervor."

#: finmel01.tra:612
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "There, there, Imoen.  I command the essence within you.  Let's see just how "
#| "much of my power you have within you, yes?"
msgid ""
"There, there, Imoen. I command the essence within you. Let's see just how "
"much of my power you have within you, yes?"
msgstr ""
"Nun los, Imoen.  Ich kontrolliere die Essenz in Euch.  Zeigt uns schon, wie "
"viel Macht in Euch steckt."

#: finmel01.tra:613
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Ahhhh, Balthazar is here as well.  How clever to deny me his essence, "
#| "<CHARNAME>.  Still blinded by your devotion to destiny, Balthazar?  Or have "
#| "you abandoned your faith so quickly?"
msgid ""
"Ahhhh, Balthazar is here as well. How clever to deny me his essence, "
"<CHARNAME>. Still blinded by your devotion to destiny, Balthazar? Or have "
"you abandoned your faith so quickly?"
msgstr ""
"Ah, Balthasar ist auch hier.  Wie geschickt, mir seine Essenz zu verweigern,"
" <CHARNAME>.  Seid Ihr immer noch geblendet von der Hingabe zu Eurem "
"Schicksal, Balthasar?  Oder habe ihr Euren Glauben so schnell aufgegeben?"

#: finmel01.tra:614
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Oh no?  Perhaps you do not understand.  This... this place, here, is the "
#| "Source.  This is where the essence of all of Bhaal's children returns when "
#| "they die, hidden away.  Did you never wonder, dear Balthazar, what killing "
#| "all the other spawn of Bhaal was *for*?"
msgid ""
"Oh no? Perhaps you do not understand. This... this place, here, is the "
"Source. This is where the essence of all of Bhaal's children returns when "
"they die, hidden away. Did you never wonder, dear Balthazar, what killing "
"all the other spawn of Bhaal was *for*?"
msgstr ""
"Oh nein?  Vielleicht versteht Ihr immer noch nicht.  Dieses hier... dieser "
"Platz ist die Quelle.  Hierher kehrt die Essenz aller Bhaal Kinder zurück, "
"wenn sie sterben.  Habt Ihr Euch niemals gefragt, mein lieber Balthasar, "
"*wofür* das Töten all der anderen Bhaalkinder nötig war?"

#: finmel01.tra:615
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "And well you should not have, though you aided me regardless.  Bhaal may, "
#| "indeed, be... somewhere.  But not here.  Here I have locked these essences "
#| "away and drank heartily of their power.  The Source, the Throne, all are "
#| "mine... and god-hood is but one simple step away."
msgid ""
"And well you should not have, though you aided me regardless. Bhaal may, "
"indeed, be... somewhere. But not here. Here I have locked these essences "
"away and drank heartily of their power. The Source, the Throne, all are "
"mine... and god-hood is but one simple step away."
msgstr ""
"Auch falls Ihr es nicht getan haben solltet, so habt Ihr mir doch "
"bedingungslos geholfen.  Bhaal mag tatsächlich irgendwo sein... aber nicht "
"hier.  Hier habe ich alle diese Essenzen gesammelt und ich trank regelmäßig "
"davon.  Diese Quelle, der Thron, alles gehört mir... und das Gott-Sein ist "
"nur einen kleinen Schritt entfernt."

#: finmel01.tra:616
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I was going to resurrect them anyway, to serve as my conquering avatars.  "
#| "And I prefer them far better this way... completely servile, obeying every "
#| "order without question."
msgid ""
"I was going to resurrect them anyway, to serve as my conquering avatars. And"
" I prefer them far better this way... completely servile, obeying every "
"order without question."
msgstr ""
"Ich hätte sie sowieso wiederbelebt, damit sie mir als meine siegreichen "
"Avatare dienen.  Und so gefallen sie mir auch viel besser... vollkommen "
"unterwürfig, jedem Befehl folgend ohne Fragen zu stellen."

#: finmel01.tra:617
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "And since you recruited Balthazar to your side, I've decided on the "
#| "delicious irony of re-creating poor, pathetic Gromnir as well.  It delights "
#| "me to no end to know that he was right about me all along... and yet it made"
#| " no difference.  You murdered him still, as I knew you would."
msgid ""
"And since you recruited Balthazar to your side, I've decided on the "
"delicious irony of re-creating poor, pathetic Gromnir as well. It delights "
"me to no end to know that he was right about me all along... and yet it made"
" no difference. You murdered him still, as I knew you would."
msgstr ""
"Nun, da Ihr Balthasar für Eure Seite gewinnen konntet, habe ich entschieden "
"- welch herrliche Ironie - den armen, jämmerlichen Gromnir ebenfalls "
"wiederauferstehen zu lassen.  Es erfreut mich ohne Ende, dass er über mich "
"die ganze Zeit Bescheid wusste... und doch hat es keinen Unterschied "
"gemacht.  Ihr ermordetet ihn trotzdem, genau wie ich es vorhergesehen habe."

#: finmel01.tra:618
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You should have kept your energies to yourself, Melissan.  Spending them on "
#| "re-creating the Five will cost you... and cost you dearly."
msgid ""
"You should have kept your energies to yourself, Melissan. Spending them on "
"re-creating the Five will cost you... and cost you dearly."
msgstr ""
"Ihr hättet Eure Energien für Euch behalten sollen, Melissan.  Sie für die "
"Wiedererschaffung der Fünf zu verwenden, wird Euch teuer zu stehen kommen..."
" sehr teuer."

#: finmel01.tra:619
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Perhaps.  But already I am immortal, which means I cannot be killed even by "
#| "you.  And there is still more of your father's essence for me to take."
msgid ""
"Perhaps. But already I am immortal, which means I cannot be killed even by "
"you. And there is still more of your father's essence for me to take."
msgstr ""
"Vielleicht.  Aber ich bin bereits unsterblich, was bedeutet, dass nicht "
"einmal Ihr mich töten könnt.  Und es existiert immer noch mehr von Eures "
"Vaters Essenz, die ich aufnehmen kann."

#: finmel01.tra:620
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "They provided a considerable challenge for you individually, <CHARNAME>.  I "
#| "wonder how you will fare against them all?"
msgid ""
"They provided a considerable challenge for you individually, <CHARNAME>. I "
"wonder how you will fare against them all?"
msgstr ""
"Schon jeder für sich alleine war eine beträchtliche Herausforderung für "
"Euch, <CHARNAME>.  Ich glaube kaum, dass Ihr gegen alle gleichzeitig "
"bestehen könnt."

#: finmel01.tra:621
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "So come, <CHARNAME>...kill your siblings once again.  If you can."
msgid "So come, <CHARNAME>...kill your siblings once again. If you can."
msgstr ""
"Nun kommt, <CHARNAME>... tötet Eure Geschwister ein weiteres Mal.  Wenn Ihr "
"könnt."

#: finmel01.tra:622
msgid "There is enough essence, in fact, even for you... Sarevok."
msgstr "Es ist genug Essenz da, sogar für Euch... Sarevok."

#: finmel01.tra:623
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "But... we don't have all your siblings accounted for just quite yet, do we?"
#| "  Haven't you forgotten someone?"
msgid ""
"But... we don't have all your siblings accounted for just quite yet, do we? "
"Haven't you forgotten someone?"
msgstr ""
"Aber... wir haben nicht alle Eure Geschwister hier versammelt, nicht wahr?  "
"Haben wir nicht jemanden vergessen?"

#: finmel01.tra:624
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Oh, but we do, Sarevok.  I made you an offer once before, and that offer "
#| "still stands.  Join me now, abandon this pathetic whelp, and take your place"
#| " at my side."
msgid ""
"Oh, but we do, Sarevok. I made you an offer once before, and that offer "
"still stands. Join me now, abandon this pathetic whelp, and take your place "
"at my side."
msgstr ""
"Aber sicher haben wir das, Sarevok.  Ich machte Euch bereits einmal ein "
"Angebot und dieses gilt immer noch.  Unterstützt mich jetzt, verlasst diesen"
" armseligen Jungen und stellt Euch auf meine Seite."

#: finmel01.tra:625
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "The geas the fool placed on your heart is nothing.  I could easily remove "
#| "it.  In fact, I do so now.  There... act as you will."
msgid ""
"The geas the fool placed on your heart is nothing. I could easily remove it."
" In fact, I do so now. There... act as you will."
msgstr ""
"Der Geas, den dieser Narr auf Euch gesprochen hat, ist nichts.  Ich kann ihn"
" mit Leichtigkeit entfernen.  In Wahrheit mache ich dieses gerade. Seht... "
"handelt nach Eurem eigenen Willen."

#: finmel01.tra:626
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Perhaps.  But you are a great warrior... and could be a fine general to lead"
#| " my earthly armies.  Power, riches, respect... all you desire.  Including "
#| "the return of the Bhaalspawn essence you lost.  Come, Sarevok... be the "
#| "demon you once were.  Serve me."
msgid ""
"Perhaps. But you are a great warrior... and could be a fine general to lead "
"my earthly armies. Power, riches, respect... all you desire. Including the "
"return of the Bhaalspawn essence you lost. Come, Sarevok... be the demon you"
" once were. Serve me."
msgstr ""
"Vielleicht. Aber Ihr seid ein großer Krieger... und ihr könntet ein "
"großartiger General sein, der meine irdischen Armeen anführt.  Macht, "
"Reichtum, Respekt... alles was Ihr wünscht.  Und natürlich die Rückkehr der "
"Bhaalessenz, die Ihr einst verloren habt.  Kommt Sarevok, seid der Dämon, "
"der Ihr einst wart.  Dient mir."

#: finmel01.tra:627
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Then fight for me you shall!  And your first victim will be the "
#| "<PRO_BROTHERSISTER> upon whom vengeance is so richly deserved!"
msgid ""
"Then fight for me you shall! And your first victim will be the "
"<PRO_BROTHERSISTER> upon whom vengeance is so richly deserved!"
msgstr ""
"Dann sollt Ihr für mich kämpfen!  Und Euer erstes Opfer soll Euer Bruder "
"sein, der Eure Vergeltung wahrhaftig verdient."

#: finmel01.tra:628
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Then die with your fool <PRO_BROTHERSISTER>, if that is your wish!  The Five"
#| " shall be the end of you both!"
msgid ""
"Then die with your fool <PRO_BROTHERSISTER>, if that is your wish! The Five "
"shall be the end of you both!"
msgstr ""
"Dann sterbt mit Eurem schwachsinnigen Bruder, wenn das Euer Wunsch ist!  Die"
" Fünf werden Euer beider Ende sein."

#: finmel01.tra:629
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I brought you here, Sarevok.  To give you a second chance.  Join me and "
#| "fight against <CHARNAME> and I will return the power you lost, the power you"
#| " crave so much.  I will make you the man you once were."
msgid ""
"I brought you here, Sarevok. To give you a second chance. Join me and fight "
"against <CHARNAME> and I will return the power you lost, the power you crave"
" so much. I will make you the man you once were."
msgstr ""
"Ich brachte Euch hierher, Sarevok.  Um Euch eine zweite Chance zu geben.  "
"Unterstützt mich und kämpft gegen <CHARNAME> und ich werde Euch die Macht "
"zurückgeben, die Ihr einst verlort, die Macht, nach der Ihr Euch so sehr "
"sehnt.  Ich werde Euch wieder zu dem Mann machen, der Ihr einst wart."

#: finmel01.tra:630
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "What--?  Mortal!  No, it can't be!  I am nearly mortal once again!  I have "
#| "lost too much power!  You shall pay for this!!"
msgid ""
"What? Mortal! No, it can't be! I am nearly mortal once again! I have lost "
"too much power! You shall pay for this!"
msgstr ""
"Was--?  Sterblich!  Nein, das kann nicht sein!  Ich bin fast wieder "
"sterblich!!  Ich habe zuviel Macht verloren!!  Dafür werdet Ihr bezahlen!!"

#: finsarev.tra:26
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Who--?  Melissan.  And <CHARNAME>, no less.  And to think that I had "
#| "resigned myself to not being a part of this little play.  Who brought me "
#| "here?  And why am I in my old armor?"
msgid ""
"Who? Melissan. And <CHARNAME>, no less. And to think that I had resigned "
"myself to not being a part of this little play. Who brought me here? And why"
" am I in my old armor?"
msgstr ""
"Wer...?  Melissan.  Und niemand anders als <CHARNAME>.  Ich hatte mich schon"
" damit abgefunden, an diesem kleinen Spiel nicht beteiligt zu sein.  Wer "
"brachte mich hierher?  Und warum in meiner alten Rüstung?"

#: finsarev.tra:27
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Fight <CHARNAME>?  Aye... I will do that."
msgid "Fight <CHARNAME>? Aye... I will do that."
msgstr "Kämpfen gegen <CHARNAME>?  Ja... das werde ich tun."

#: finsarev.tra:28
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "So you die again, as well.  It's all good."
msgid "So you die again, as well. It's all good."
msgstr "So sterbt Ihr denn ein weiteres Mal.  Auch gut."

#: finsarev.tra:29
msgid "You're a fool, Sarevok, if you think you'll make any difference."
msgstr ""
"Ihr seid ein Narr, Sarevok, wenn Ihr denkt, dass dieses irgendeinen "
"Unterschied macht."

#: finsarev.tra:30
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You're willing to become Melissan's servant, now?  I'm disappointed."
msgid "You're willing to become Melissan's servant, now? I'm disappointed."
msgstr ""
"Ihr seid also bereit, Melissan´s Diener zu werden?  Ich bin enttäuscht von "
"Euch."

#: finsarev.tra:31
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Then you'll die.  I gave you life again, and I can take it away... for the "
#| "third time."
msgid ""
"Then you'll die. I gave you life again, and I can take it away... for the "
"third time."
msgstr ""
"So werdet Ihr sterben.  Ich gab Euch Euer Leben zurück, und ich kann es Euch"
" auch wieder nehmen... zum dritten Mal dann."

#: finsarev.tra:32
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "It is true.  I may die again at your hand, <CHARNAME>.  But better that than"
#| " sit in your shadow and taste the bile in my heart while you take what was "
#| "once rightfully mine.  Better to fight for Melissan than suffer that."
msgid ""
"It is true. I may die again at your hand, <CHARNAME>. But better that than "
"sit in your shadow and taste the bile in my heart while you take what was "
"once rightfully mine. Better to fight for Melissan than suffer that."
msgstr ""
"Ja, es ist wahr.  Vielleicht sterbe ich ein weiteres Mal durch Eure Hand, "
"<CHARNAME>.  Aber das ist besser, als in Eurem Schatten zu sitzen und den "
"Schmerz in meinem Herzen zu spüren, während Ihr nehmt, was einst rechtmäßig "
"mir gehörte.  Besser für Melissan kämpfen, als dieses zu ertragen."

#: finsol01.tra:580
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Only one other spawn of the dead god remains... the sibling who fought at "
#| "your side.  His portion of the essence is less than your own, but still "
#| "significant.  His choice must also be made."
msgid ""
"Only one other spawn of the dead god remains... the sibling who fought at "
"your side. His portion of the essence is less than your own, but still "
"significant. His choice must also be made."
msgstr ""
"Nur ein anderer Nachkomme des toten Gottes bleibt übrig... der Bruder, der "
"an Eurer Seite kämpfte.  Sein Anteil an der Essenz ist geringer als der "
"Eure, aber nicht unbedeutend.  Er muss sich ebenfalls entscheiden."

#: finsol01.tra:581
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "First, however, there is the matter of the children of the dead god who "
#| "fought by your side.  Their essences are less than your own, but their "
#| "decision no less important."
msgid ""
"First, however, there is the matter of the children of the dead god who "
"fought by your side. Their essences are less than your own, but their "
"decision no less important."
msgstr ""
"Zuerst aber sind da die Belange der Kinder des toten Gottes, die an Eurer "
"Seite gekämpft haben.  Ihre Essenzen sind geringer als die Eure, aber ihre "
"Entscheidung ist nicht weniger wichtig."

#: finsol01.tra:582
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I am merely an agent of the universe in this matter, Balthazar.  I am "
#| "charged to see the destiny of the children of Bhaal brought to its "
#| "conclusion.  You have an opportunity that few are given.  You may choose "
#| "your destiny... a choice you thought yourself forever denied."
msgid ""
"I am merely an agent of the universe in this matter, Balthazar. I am charged"
" to see the destiny of the children of Bhaal brought to its conclusion. You "
"have an opportunity that few are given. You may choose your destiny... a "
"choice you thought yourself forever denied."
msgstr ""
"Ich bin lediglich ein Vertreter des Universums in dieser Angelegenheit, "
"Balthasar.  Mir wurde aufgetragen, das Schicksal der Bhaalkinder zu seinem "
"Abschluss zu bringen.  Ihr habt eine Möglichkeit, die wenigen gegeben ist.  "
"Ihr könnt Euer Schicksal wählen... eine Wahl, die Ihr Euch für alle "
"Ewigkeiten verwehrt saht."

#: finsol01.tra:583
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "If that is your choice, you may surrender the portion of your divine essence"
#| " to your elder sibling.  You may become a normal mortal, with a destiny to "
#| "follow as you see fit."
msgid ""
"If that is your choice, you may surrender the portion of your divine essence"
" to your elder sibling. You may become a normal mortal, with a destiny to "
"follow as you see fit."
msgstr ""
"Wenn das Eure Wahl ist, so könnt Ihr Euren Teil der göttlichen Essenz an "
"Euren Bruder übergeben.  Ihr werdet ein normaler Sterblicher sein und könnt "
"Eurem Schicksal folgen, wie Ihr es für nötig erachtet."

#: finsol01.tra:584
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "As you wish, Balthazar, so it is done.  Go in peace, and know that in the "
#| "end you walked that narrow path which had ever eluded you."
msgid ""
"As you wish, Balthazar, so it is done. Go in peace, and know that in the end"
" you walked that narrow path which had ever eluded you."
msgstr ""
"Wie Ihr wollt, Balthasar, so ist es geschehen.  Geht in Frieden, und wisst, "
"dass Ihr schließlich den Weg geht, der Euch immer unmöglich erschien."

#: finsol01.tra:585
msgid "Now there is but one other sibling who must also make her choice."
msgstr ""
"Nun ist da nur noch Eure Schwester, die ebenfalls Ihre Entscheidung treffen "
"muss."

#: finsol01.tra:586
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "While it fills me with distaste that you would even bring such a creature of"
#| " evil before me, god-child, you must remember that in this place an oath is "
#| "worth more than the words with which it is spoken.  You are no god yet... "
#| "and while I would rather destroy this undead thing, it now falls on me to "
#| "enforce the promise you have made."
msgid ""
"While it fills me with distaste that you would even bring such a creature of"
" evil before me, god-child, you must remember that in this place an oath is "
"worth more than the words with which it is spoken. You are no god yet... and"
" while I would rather destroy this undead thing, it now falls on me to "
"enforce the promise you have made."
msgstr ""
"Obwohl es mich mit Ekel erfüllt, dass Ihr eine solche Kreatur des Bösen zu "
"mir gebracht habt, Gottkind, so muss ich Euch dennoch daran erinnern, dass "
"ein Versprechen an diesem Ort mehr ist als nur die Worte, mit denen es "
"gegeben wurde.  Ihr seid noch kein Gott... und obwohl ich dieses untote Ding"
" lieber zerstören würde, so muss ich doch für die Einhaltung des "
"Versprechens, welches Ihr gegeben habt, sorgen."

#: imoen25j.tra:476 imoen25p.tra:476
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I'm not going anywhere with you!  And nobody's touching my soul!  Not "
#| "again!!"
msgid ""
"I'm not going anywhere with you! And nobody's touching my soul! Not again!"
msgstr ""
"Ich gehe nirgendwo mit Euch hin!  Und niemand greift nach meiner Seele!  "
"Nicht wieder!!"

#: imoen25p.tra:470
#, fuzzy
#| msgctxt "IMOEN18"
#| msgid ""
#| "Nnngh!  Ah, it hurts!  <CHARNAME>, stop her... it... it hurts!!"
msgctxt "IMOEN18"
msgid "Nnngh! Ah, it hurts! <CHARNAME>, stop her... it... it hurts!"
msgstr ""
"Neein! Aaah, es tut weh!  <CHARNAME>, stoppt sie...es...es tut so weh!!"

#: imoen25p.tra:471
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "What are you doing to her?!  Stop it, I demand it!!"
msgid "What are you doing to her?! Stop it, I demand it!"
msgstr "Was macht Ihr mit ihr?!  Hört damit auf, ich befehle es!!"

#: imoen25p.tra:472
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "I'm the one you're after, Melissan!  Leave her alone!!"
msgid "I'm the one you're after, Melissan! Leave her alone!"
msgstr ""
"Ich bin derjenige, hinter dem Ihr her seid, Melissan!  Lasst sie in Ruhe!!"

#: imoen25p.tra:473
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Pull yourself together, Imoen!  Attack!!"
msgid "Pull yourself together, Imoen! Attack!"
msgstr "Reist Euch zusammen, Imoen!  Greift an!!"

#: imoen25p.tra:474
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "So what do I care about Imoen?  Kill her, Melissan."
msgid "So what do I care about Imoen? Kill her, Melissan."
msgstr "Was geht mich Imoen an?  Tötet sie, Melissan."

#: imoen25p.tra:475
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Wh-what... where am I?  What's going on?  <CHARNAME>?"
msgid "Wh-what... where am I? What's going on? <CHARNAME>?"
msgstr "Wwwas... wo bin ich?  Was passiert hier?  <CHARNAME>?"

#: imoen25p.tra:477
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "It... it's gone... I'm human again.  Ohhhh, now I know what you went "
#| "through, <CHARNAME>!  I don't know if I ever want to go through that again!"
msgid ""
"It... it's gone... I'm human again. Ohhhh, now I know what you went through,"
" <CHARNAME>! I don't know if I ever want to go through that again!"
msgstr ""
"Es... es ist vorbei.  Ich bin wieder menschlich.  Ohhh, jetzt weiß ich, was "
"Ihr durchgemacht habt, <CHARNAME>!  Ich bezweifle, dass ich das noch einmal "
"erleben möchte!"

#: imoen25p.tra:478
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "And I can't believe what you said, either!  'Go ahead and kill her'?  After "
#| "all we've been through, that's what you say in my defense?!"
msgid ""
"And I can't believe what you said, either! 'Go ahead and kill her'? After "
"all we've been through, that's what you say in my defense?!"
msgstr ""
"Und ich kann nicht glauben, was Ihr gesagt habt!  \"Macht nur, tötet sie\"?"
"  Nach allem, was wir durchgestanden haben, sagt Ihr das zu meiner "
"Verteidigung?"

#: imoen25p.tra:479
msgid "I was trying to convince Melissan to leave you alone, Imoen!"
msgstr ""
"Ich habe versucht, Melissan zu überzeugen, Euch in Ruhe zu lassen, Imoen!"

#: imoen25p.tra:480
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Get over yourself, little girl.  I never asked you to come, did I?"
msgid "Get over yourself, little girl. I never asked you to come, did I?"
msgstr ""
"Kriegt Euch wieder ein, Kleine.  Ich hab Euch nie darum gebeten mitzukommen."

#: imoen25p.tra:481
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "We don't have time for this chat, Imoen!  This is the middle of a fight!"
msgid ""
"We don't have time for this chat, Imoen! This is the middle of a fight!"
msgstr ""
"Wir haben keine Zeit zum Plaudern, Imoen!  Wir sind hier mitten in einem "
"Kampf!"

#: imoen25p.tra:482
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Well... I suppose.  You convinced me more than her, obviously.  I... I'm "
#| "just glad I didn't do more damage as the slayer.  I don't know how you "
#| "handled it.  Thank you for... for not killing me."
msgid ""
"Well... I suppose. You convinced me more than her, obviously. I... I'm just "
"glad I didn't do more damage as the slayer. I don't know how you handled it."
" Thank you for... for not killing me."
msgstr ""
"Nun... mag sein.  Ihr habt mich offensichtlich mehr überzeugt als sie.  "
"Ich... ich bin nur froh, dass ich als Schlächter nicht mehr Schaden "
"angerichtet habe.  Ich weiß nicht, wie Ihr damit fertig geworden seid.  "
"Danke, dass Ihr mich nicht... nicht getötet habt."

#: imoen25p.tra:483
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I... I can't stay here, though.  This is way out of my league.  I wish you "
#| "well, <CHARNAME>, and I hope I'll see you again.  Maybe back at Candlekeep, "
#| "huh?  Anyway... good luck..."
msgid ""
"I... I can't stay here, though. This is way out of my league. I wish you "
"well, <CHARNAME>, and I hope I'll see you again. Maybe back at Candlekeep, "
"huh? Anyway... good luck..."
msgstr ""
"Ich... ich kann jedoch nicht hier bleiben.  Hier wird in einer höheren Liga "
"gespielt.  Ich wünsche Euch alles Gute, <CHARNAME>, und ich hoffe, ich sehe "
"Euch wieder.  Vielleicht in Kerzenburg, hmmm? Auf jeden Fall... viel "
"Glück..."

#: imoen25p.tra:484
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Do you need me to join back up with you?  I could... leave the Throne, I "
#| "think... I think I have that power, now, same as you.  But I'll fight by "
#| "your side again, if you want me to."
msgid ""
"Do you need me to join back up with you? I could... leave the Throne, I "
"think... I think I have that power, now, same as you. But I'll fight by your"
" side again, if you want me to."
msgstr ""
"Braucht Ihr mich wieder, damit ich mich Euch anschließe?  Ich könnte... den "
"Thron verlassen, denke ich... Ich denke, ich habe die Macht jetzt, dieselbe "
"wie Ihr.  Aber ich kämpfe wieder an Eurer Seite, wenn Ihr das wollt."

#: imoen25p.tra:485
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Imoen Has Survived\n"
#| "\n"
#| "Imoen managed to survive Melissan's attempt to force her into berserk Slayer form.  It seems that in doing so, Imoen has had her own progress in the taint advanced considerably.  She now not only can turn into the same Slayer form that I began to back in Spellhold... but has also gained the ability to go ethereal for brief periods of time.\n"
#| "\n"
#| "Ethereal\n"
#| "-------------\n"
#| "Imoen is now able to enter the Ethereal Plane for brief periods of time.  The ability is useable once every minute, and its use prevents her from assuming the Slayer form for a minute, as well.  Imoen can remain fully ethereal and intangible to forces on this plane for a full round... during which she is invisible and completely immune to harm.  During that round, she also cannot cast spells or use abilities.\n"
#| "For another two rounds afterwards, Imoen can remain 'half-phased'...she is partially ethereal and partially in this plane.  She is still invisible, but takes half damage from all sources.  In this state, there is a small chance (10%) that she will miscast a spell.  For all three rounds, she is able to see any invisible targets."
msgid ""
"Imoen Has Survived\n"
"\n"
"Imoen managed to survive Melissan's attempt to force her into berserk Slayer form. It seems that in doing so, Imoen has had her own progress in the taint advanced considerably. She now not only can turn into the same Slayer form that I began to back in Spellhold... but has also gained the ability to go ethereal for brief periods of time.\n"
"\n"
"Ethereal\n"
"-------------\n"
"Imoen is now able to enter the Ethereal Plane for brief periods of time. The ability is useable once every minute, and its use prevents her from assuming the Slayer form for a minute, as well. Imoen can remain fully ethereal and intangible to forces on this plane for a full round... during which she is invisible and completely immune to harm. During that round, she also cannot cast spells or use abilities.\n"
"For another two rounds afterwards, Imoen can remain 'half-phased'...she is partially ethereal and partially in this plane. She is still invisible, but takes half damage from all sources. In this state, there is a small chance (10%) that she will miscast a spell. For all three rounds, she is able to see any invisible targets."
msgstr ""
"Imoen hat überlebt\n"
"\n"
"Imoen hat es geschafft zu überleben, als Melissan versuchte, sie in die Gestalt des Berserkerschlächters zu zwingen.  Es scheint, als sei Imoen dadurch in ihrem Makel ein großes Stück vorangeschritten.  Sie kann sich nicht nur in dieselbe Schlächtergestalt verwandeln, die bei mir damals in der Zauberfeste erschien... sondern sie erhielt auch die Fähigkeit, für kurze Zeit ätherisch zu werden.\n"
"\n"
"Ätherisch\n"
"-------------\n"
"Imoen ist es nun möglich, für kurze Zeit die Ätherische Ebene zu betreten.  Diese Fähigkeit kann einmal pro Minute benutzt werden, und sie wird dadurch ebenfalls für eine Minute daran gehindert, die Gestalt des Schlächters anzunehmen.  Imoen kann für eine Runde völlig ätherisch und unerreichbar für Kräfte dieser Ebene werden.  In dieser Zeit ist sie unsichtbar und vollständig immun gegenüber schädlichen Einflüssen; sie kann aber auch keine Zauber sprechen oder andere Fähigkeiten einsetzen.\n"
"Für zwei weitere Runden danach kann Imoen \"halbzerteilt\" sein: sie ist teilweise ätherisch und teilweise auf dieser Ebene.  Sie ist immer noch unsichtbar, erleidet aber halben Schaden von allen Angriffen.  In diesem Zustand besteht eine geringe Chance (10%), dass ein von ihr gesprochener Zauber versagt.  In allen drei Runden kann sie alle unsichtbaren Ziele sehen."

#: imoen25p.tra:486
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Sure.  Let's join up again."
msgid "Sure. Let's join up again."
msgstr "Klar.  Lasst uns gemeinsam weitermachen."

#: imoen25p.tra:487
msgid "No... get out of here while you can, Imoen."
msgstr "Nein... verschwindet von hier, solange Ihr könnt, Imoen."

#: imoen25p.tra:488
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I wish you well, <CHARNAME>, and I hope I'll see you again.  Maybe back at "
#| "Candlekeep, huh?  Anyway... good luck..."
msgid ""
"I wish you well, <CHARNAME>, and I hope I'll see you again. Maybe back at "
"Candlekeep, huh? Anyway... good luck..."
msgstr ""
"Ich wünsche Euch alles Gute, <CHARNAME>, und ich hoffe, ich sehe Euch "
"wieder.  Vielleicht in Kerzenburg, hmmm? Auf jeden Fall... viel Glück..."

#: imoen25p.tra:489
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Yeah, right.  You do whatever you have to, <CHARNAME>.  Me... I'm getting as"
#| " far away from here as possible.  Good-bye!"
msgid ""
"Yeah, right. You do whatever you have to, <CHARNAME>. Me... I'm getting as "
"far away from here as possible. Good-bye!"
msgstr ""
"Ja, richtig.  Ihr tut, was Ihr tun müsst, <CHARNAME>.  Ich... ich "
"verschwinde so weit wie möglich von hier. Lebt wohl!"

#: imoen25p.tra:490
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Nope, you sure didn't.  Thanks for nothing, I guess.  You do whatever you "
#| "have to, <CHARNAME>.  Me... I'm getting as far away from here as possible.  "
#| "Good-bye!"
msgid ""
"Nope, you sure didn't. Thanks for nothing, I guess. You do whatever you have"
" to, <CHARNAME>. Me... I'm getting as far away from here as possible. Good-"
"bye!"
msgstr ""
"Nee!  Klar habt Ihr nicht.  Danke für nichts, nehme ich an.  Ihr tut, was "
"Ihr tun müsst, <CHARNAME>.  Ich... ich verschwinde so weit wie möglich von "
"hier.  Lebt wohl!"

#: imoen25p.tra:491
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I'm... just glad I didn't do anything worse while I was... when I... oh, I "
#| "just don't know how you handled it back in Spellhold.  Thank you for... not "
#| "killing me, okay?"
msgid ""
"I'm... just glad I didn't do anything worse while I was... when I... oh, I "
"just don't know how you handled it back in Spellhold. Thank you for... not "
"killing me, okay?"
msgstr ""
"Ich bin... einfach froh, dass ich nichts Schlimmeres getan habe, während "
"ich... als ich... oh, ich weiß einfach nicht, wie Ihr damals in der "
"Zauberfeste damit umgegangen seid.  Danke, dass Ihr... mich nicht getötet "
"habt, okay?"

#: imoen25p.tra:492
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
