msgid ""
"I see the fight's still going on. Do you need me back in the party? I "
"could... leave the Throne, I think... I think I have that power, now, same "
"as you. But I'd like to see this through, same as you."
msgstr ""
"Ich sehe, dass der Kampf noch nicht zu Ende ist.  Braucht Ihr mich wieder in"
" der Gruppe?  Ich könnte... den Thron verlassen, denke ich... Ich denke, ich"
" habe die Macht jetzt, dieselbe wie Ihr.  Aber ich kämpfe wieder an Eurer "
"Seite, wenn Ihr das wollt."

#: imoen25p.tra:494
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Stop distracting me in the middle of combat, already!  Get back in the "
#| "party!"
msgid ""
"Stop distracting me in the middle of combat, already! Get back in the party!"
msgstr ""
"Hört schon auf, mich mitten im Kampf abzulenken!  Geht zurück zur Gruppe!"

#: imoen25p.tra:495
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Yes <PRO_SIRMAAM>!  (giggle!)  Time to kick a certain someone's butt, right?"
msgid ""
"Yes <PRO_SIRMAAM>! (giggle!) Time to kick a certain someone's butt, right?"
msgstr ""
"Jawohl,  <PRO_SIRMAAM>! (kichert) Zeit, jemandem in den Hintern zu treten, "
"ja?"

#: irenic2.tra:435
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Indeed.  We meet once again."
msgid "Indeed. We meet once again."
msgstr "In der Tat.  So treffen wir uns also wieder."

#: irenic2.tra:436
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "That's okay.  If Sarevok can turn up like a bad penny, then you're allowed "
#| "to, as well."
msgid ""
"That's okay. If Sarevok can turn up like a bad penny, then you're allowed "
"to, as well."
msgstr ""
"Das ist schon in Ordnung.  Wenn Sarevok wie ein falscher Fünfziger wieder "
"auftauchen kann, so sei es Euch ebenso erlaubt."

#: irenic2.tra:437
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You told her how to influence me, didn't you?  And you told her I was in "
#| "Suldanessalar."
msgid ""
"You told her how to influence me, didn't you? And you told her I was in "
"Suldanessalar."
msgstr ""
"Ihr habt ihr erzählt, wie man mich beeinflussen kann?  Und ihr habt ihr "
"erzählt, dass ich in Suldanessallar war?"

#: irenic2.tra:438
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You're a pathetic excuse for an elf, Irenicus.  If you wish to die again, "
#| "I'll happily oblige."
msgid ""
"You're a pathetic excuse for an elf, Irenicus. If you wish to die again, "
"I'll happily oblige."
msgstr ""
"Ihr seid die erbärmliche Entschuldigung für einen Elfen, Irenicus.  Wenn Ihr"
" wünscht, ein zweites Mal zu sterben, so stehe ich gerne zur Verfügung."

#: irenic2.tra:439
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You're collecting my leavings, Melissan?  How very sad for you."
msgid "You're collecting my leavings, Melissan? How very sad for you."
msgstr ""
"Ihr sammelt auf, was ich zurücklasse, Melissan?  Wie traurig für Euch."

#: irenic2.tra:440
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "So, <CHARNAME>...it is now just you and I, once again.  At odds in the "
#| "bowels of Hell and preparing to do combat.  How very fitting."
msgid ""
"So, <CHARNAME>...it is now just you and I, once again. At odds in the bowels"
" of Hell and preparing to do combat. How very fitting."
msgstr ""
"So, <CHARNAME>... wieder einmal stehen wir uns gegenüber, Ihr und ich.  "
"Gegenüber in den Eingeweiden der Hölle und in Vorbereitung auf den Kampf.  "
"Passend, nicht wahr?"

#: irenic2.tra:441
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "This fight is mine, Irenicus.  While you stewed in Hell, my power has "
#| "multiplied."
msgid ""
"This fight is mine, Irenicus. While you stewed in Hell, my power has "
"multiplied."
msgstr ""
"Dieser Kampf gehört mir, Irenicus.  Während Ihr in der Hölle schmortet, "
"haben sich meine Kräfte vervielfacht."

#: irenic2.tra:442
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You actually think you'll stop me?  It appears your delusions have survived "
#| "the many beatings at my hand."
msgid ""
"You actually think you'll stop me? It appears your delusions have survived "
"the many beatings at my hand."
msgstr ""
"Ihr glaubt tatsächlich, dass Ihr mich stoppen könnt?  Es scheint, als ob "
"Eure Wahnvorstellungen die vielen Niederlagen unbeschadet überdauert haben."

#: irenic2.tra:443
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "So you're actually willing to serve as Melissan's little lackey?  I would "
#| "expect more from the great elven magician.  Ellesime would be sad to see you"
#| " reduced to this."
msgid ""
"So you're actually willing to serve as Melissan's little lackey? I would "
"expect more from the great elven magician. Ellesime would be sad to see you "
"reduced to this."
msgstr ""
"So seid Ihr tatsächlich bereit, als Melissans kleiner Lakai zu dienen?  Ich "
"hätte mehr erwartet vom großen Elfenmagier.  Ellesime wäre enttäuscht, Euch "
"so tief gesunken zu sehen."

#: irenic2.tra:444
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Don't you ever tire of that bravado?  Haven't you received enough spankings "
#| "upon my knee?"
msgid ""
"Don't you ever tire of that bravado? Haven't you received enough spankings "
"upon my knee?"
msgstr ""
"Werdet Ihr niemals Eurer Prahlerei überdrüssig?  Habt Ihr immer noch nicht "
"genug Prügel bekommen?"

#: irenic2.tra:445
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You won't stop me, Irenicus.  Nobody can.  My destiny is at hand."
msgid "You won't stop me, Irenicus. Nobody can. My destiny is at hand."
msgstr ""
"Ihr könnt mich nicht aufhaltet, Irenicus.  Niemand kann es. Meine Bestimmung"
" erfüllt sich."

#: irenic2.tra:446
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "It appears you have been the beneficiary of low expectations, but even I "
#| "have learned from my mistakes.  Here, I have nothing to lose, not even my "
#| "life.  Thanks to Melissan, I still have time to snuff out your divine "
#| "ascencion personally. We will be even!"
msgid ""
"It appears you have been the beneficiary of low expectations, but even I "
"have learned from my mistakes. Here, I have nothing to lose, not even my "
"life. Thanks to Melissan, I still have time to snuff out your divine "
"ascencion personally. We will be even!"
msgstr ""
"Es scheint, dass Ihr Nutznießer sehr niedriger Erwartungen seid, aber sogar "
"ich habe aus meinen Fehlern gelernt.  Hier habe ich nichts zu verlieren, "
"nicht einmal mein Leben.  Dank Melissan habe ich immer noch die Gelegenheit,"
" Euren göttlichen Aufstieg auszulöschen.  Wir werden quitt sein!"

#: irenic2.tra:447
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You may have gained some crude and rudimentary control over your abilities "
#| "in the interim, but even I have learned a thing or two... delusions or no.  "
#| "And Melissan has given me the opportunity to personally see an end to your "
#| "ascension... consider it a favor returned."
msgid ""
"You may have gained some crude and rudimentary control over your abilities "
"in the interim, but even I have learned a thing or two... delusions or no. "
"And Melissan has given me the opportunity to personally see an end to your "
"ascension... consider it a favor returned."
msgstr ""
"Ihr mögt inzwischen eine grobe und rudimentäre Kontrolle über Eure "
"Fähigkeiten entwickelt haben, aber auch ich habe ein oder zwei Dinge "
"gelernt... Wahnvorstellung oder nicht.  Und Melissan gab mir die "
"Möglichkeit, persönlich das Ende Eures Aufstiegs zu sehen... seht es einfach"
" als das Begleichen einer alten Rechnung."

#: irenic2.tra:448
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Do not speak her name, dog.  Ellesime will understand the fullness of her "
#| "regret soon enough.  As for you... Melissan has given me the opportunity to "
#| "return an old favor.  One ascension for another... it rings with universal "
#| "justice."
msgid ""
"Do not speak her name, dog. Ellesime will understand the fullness of her "
"regret soon enough. As for you... Melissan has given me the opportunity to "
"return an old favor. One ascension for another... it rings with universal "
"justice."
msgstr ""
"Sprecht nicht ihren Namen, Hund.  Ellesime wird die Vollständigkeit ihres "
"Bedauerns bald genug erfahren.  Und zu Euch... Melissan gab mir die "
"Möglichkeit, eine alte Rechnung zu begleichen. Einen Aufstieg für einen "
"anderen... das klingt nach wirklicher Gerechtigkeit."

#: irenic2.tra:449
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "How very glib and typical.  How far the expectations of the universe must "
#| "have lowered to allow a gnat like you to even come this far.  It is "
#| "fortunate that I have an opportunity, then, to repay your termination of my "
#| "own ascension in kind."
msgid ""
"How very glib and typical. How far the expectations of the universe must "
"have lowered to allow a gnat like you to even come this far. It is fortunate"
" that I have an opportunity, then, to repay your termination of my own "
"ascension in kind."
msgstr ""
"Wie schlagfertig und doch typisch.  Wie weit müssen die Hoffungen der Welt "
"gesunken sein, dass es einem Wurm wie Euch erlaubt ist, so weit zu kommen.  "
"Glücklicherweise aber habe ich dann die Möglichkeit, Euch die Beendigung "
"meines eigenen Aufstiegs zurückzuzahlen."

#: irenic2.tra:450
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Ah, yes.  Familiar words.  Similar to the ones I spoke at the cusp of my own"
#| " ascension.  How I would enjoy to repay that favor in kind and show the "
#| "universe what an unworthy gnat you truly are."
msgid ""
"Ah, yes. Familiar words. Similar to the ones I spoke at the cusp of my own "
"ascension. How I would enjoy to repay that favor in kind and show the "
"universe what an unworthy gnat you truly are."
msgstr ""
"Ah, ja. Bekannte Worte. Ähnlich denen, die Ich selbst am Scheidepunkt meines"
" eigenen Aufstiegs sprach.  Wie würde ich es genießen, dieses mit gleicher "
"Münze zurückzuzahlen, und der ganzen Welt zu zeigen, welch verächtlicher "
"Wurm Ihr in Wahrheit seid."

#: irenic2.tra:451
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "But enough of this.  Though I would dearly love to let my sister rot in her "
#| "own Hell for eternity, it would not be a true and fitting re-union if I did "
#| "not use my new power to send her an invitation."
msgid ""
"But enough of this. Though I would dearly love to let my sister rot in her "
"own Hell for eternity, it would not be a true and fitting re-union if I did "
"not use my new power to send her an invitation."
msgstr ""
"Aber genug davon. Obwohl ich es wahrhaftig lieben würde, meine Schwester in "
"ihrer eigenen Hölle für alle Ewigkeiten verrotten zu lassen, so wäre es doch"
" keine wirkliches und passendes Wiedersehen, wenn ich meine neuen Kräfte "
"nicht nutzen würde, um ihr eine Einladung zu schicken."

#: irenic2.tra:452
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Do not overestimate your usefulness to me, 'dear' sister... nor the extent "
#| "of my non-existent affection.  Or do you truly think I had forgotten your "
#| "whispered urgings which had led me down the path of my exile?"
msgid ""
"Do not overestimate your usefulness to me, 'dear' sister... nor the extent "
"of my non-existent affection. Or do you truly think I had forgotten your "
"whispered urgings which had led me down the path of my exile?"
msgstr ""
"Überschätzt weder Eure Nützlichkeit für mich, 'liebe' Schwester... noch die "
"Ausmaße meiner nicht existierenden Zuneigung.  Oder glaubt Ihr wirklich, Ich"
" hätte Euer heimliches Drängen vergessen, was mich erst auf den Pfad meiner "
"Verbannung geführt hat?"

#: irenic2.tra:453
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Enough, sister.  We do as Melissan bids, with her servants at our side.  "
#| "Take delight, if you will, at the revenge we shall now taste.  Let us see, "
#| "<CHARNAME>, if I can rip that soul out of you once more.  I would so delight"
#| " in stealing your proud destiny a second time."
msgid ""
"Enough, sister. We do as Melissan bids, with her servants at our side. Take "
"delight, if you will, at the revenge we shall now taste. Let us see, "
"<CHARNAME>, if I can rip that soul out of you once more. I would so delight "
"in stealing your proud destiny a second time."
msgstr ""
"Genug, Schwester, wir tun, wie Melissan geheißen hat, mit ihren Dienern an "
"unserer Seite.  Wenn Ihr wollt, so habt Vergnügen an der Rache, die wir nun "
"nehmen werden.  Wollen wir doch einmal sehen, <CHARNAME>, ob ich diese Seele"
" ein zweites Mal aus Eurem Körper herausreißen kann.  Wie würde ich es "
"genießen, Eure stolze Bestimmung ein zweites Mal zu stehlen."

#: irenic2.tra:454
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You over-step your bounds, as always.  I did not call you here to rejoice in"
#| " your venom, Bodhi.  Do you not notice where we are?  Whom we face?"
msgid ""
"You over-step your bounds, as always. I did not call you here to rejoice in "
"your venom, Bodhi. Do you not notice where we are? Whom we face?"
msgstr ""
"Ihr überschreitet Eure Grenzen, wie immer.  Ich habe Euch nicht gerufen, um "
"Euer Gift zu verspritzen, Bodhi.  Seht Ihr nicht, wo wir sind?  Und wem wir "
"gegenüber stehen?"

#: irenic2.tra:455
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You think to betray me, Bodhi?  Foolish girl.  Melissan is the one who holds"
#| " power here, and you hope to find succor at the feet of this fool "
#| "<PRO_GIRLBOY>?  Stand by me or die with <PRO_HIMHER>!"
msgid ""
"You think to betray me, Bodhi? Foolish girl. Melissan is the one who holds "
"power here, and you hope to find succor at the feet of this fool "
"<PRO_GIRLBOY>? Stand by me or die with <PRO_HIMHER>!"
msgstr ""
"Ihr versucht mich zu betrügen, Bodhi?  Törichtes Mädchen.  Melissan ist "
"diejenige, die die Macht in Händen hält, und Ihr glaubt Beistand zu Füssen "
"dieses armseligen Jungen zu finden?  Haltet zu mir oder sterbt mit "
"<PRO_HIMHER>!"

#: irenic2.tra:456
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "So my ungrateful sister, you finally stand by my side.  I shall deal with "
#| "your treachery afterwards.  As for you,  <CHARNAME>, Mellisan has granted me"
#| " the power to rip the divinity from your body.  The first thing I shall feel"
#| " in an eon shall be pleasure as I watch your corpse turn to dust."
msgid ""
"So my ungrateful sister, you finally stand by my side. I shall deal with "
"your treachery afterwards. As for you, <CHARNAME>, Mellisan has granted me "
"the power to rip the divinity from your body. The first thing I shall feel "
"in an eon shall be pleasure as I watch your corpse turn to dust."
msgstr ""
"Meine undankbare Schwester, so steht Ihr mir schließlich doch zur Seite.  Um"
" Eure Falschheit werde ich mich später kümmern.  Nun aber zu Euch, "
"<CHARNAME>, Melissan gab mir die Macht, die Göttlichkeit aus Eurem Körper zu"
" reißen. Das erste, was ich nach Äonen wieder fühlen möchte, soll Vergnügen "
"sein... Vergnügen, wenn Ich Euren Körper zu Staub zerfallen sehe."

#: irenic2.tra:457
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "I see.  So you leave me, sister, just as *she* left me."
msgid "I see. So you leave me, sister, just as *she* left me."
msgstr "Also verlasst Ihr mich, Schwester, so wie *sie* mich verlassen hat."

#: irenic2.tra:458
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "It is no matter.  Melissan has given me power enough, and her own servants "
#| "shall teach you the error of your ways.  I shall strip the divinity from "
#| "<CHARNAME>'s soul and you, *dear* sister, shall be nothing but dust beside "
#| "<PRO_HIMHER>."
msgid ""
"It is no matter. Melissan has given me power enough, and her own servants "
"shall teach you the error of your ways. I shall strip the divinity from "
"<CHARNAME>'s soul and you, *dear* sister, shall be nothing but dust beside "
"<PRO_HIMHER>."
msgstr ""
"Es ist egal.  Melissan gab mir genug Macht, und ihre Diener werden Euch den "
"Irrtum Eurer eigenen Entscheidung lehren.  Ich aber werde die Göttlichkeit "
"aus <CHARNAME>'s Seele heraus reißen und Ihr, *liebe* Schwester, sollt "
"nichts anderes sein als Staub neben <PRO_HIMHER>."

#: irenic2.tra:459
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Better that than a laughable fool whose most promising idea to dominate the "
#| "Sword Coast was to 'poison' its supply of iron.  I discarded you as a "
#| "candidate long before <CHARNAME> soundly defeated you merely for fear of "
#| "losing all common sense merely by association with your pathetic soul."
msgid ""
"Better that than a laughable fool whose most promising idea to dominate the "
"Sword Coast was to 'poison' its supply of iron. I discarded you as a "
"candidate long before <CHARNAME> soundly defeated you merely for fear of "
"losing all common sense merely by association with your pathetic soul."
msgstr ""
"Besser noch als ein lächerlicher Narr, dessen vielversprechendste Idee, die "
"Schwertküste zu dominieren, es war, ihr Eisenvorkommen zu 'vergiften'. Ich "
"hatte Euch, lange bevor <CHARNAME> Euch vernichtete, als Kandidaten "
"aussortiert aus Furcht, durch eine Verbindung mit Eurer armseligen Seele "
"sämtlichen Verstand zu verlieren."

#: irenic2.tra:460
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Bark if you wish, mongrel.  Whatever dull fangs you might have possessed "
#| "have long since been pulled.  If a has-been wishes to ride <CHARNAME>'s "
#| "coat-tails it makes no difference to me... but you'll be disintegrated right"
#| " along with <PRO_HIMHER>."
msgid ""
"Bark if you wish, mongrel. Whatever dull fangs you might have possessed have"
" long since been pulled. If a has-been wishes to ride <CHARNAME>'s coat-"
"tails it makes no difference to me... but you'll be disintegrated right "
"along with <PRO_HIMHER>."
msgstr ""
"Bellt soviel Ihr wollt, Köter.  Welche Giftzähne auch immer Ihr besessen "
"haben mögt, lange schon sind sie Euch gezogen worden.  Wenn ein in "
"Vergessenheit geratener sich an <CHARNAME>'s Rockzipfel hängen will, so "
"macht dieses für mich keinen Unterschied... Ihr aber werdet zusammen mit "
"<PRO_HIMHER> ausgelöscht werden."

#: meliss01.tra:419
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Oh, please.  I saw you coming from a mile away.  I just played along because"
#| " I had no choice."
msgid ""
"Oh, please. I saw you coming from a mile away. I just played along because I"
" had no choice."
msgstr ""
"Oh, bitte. Euer Plan war offensichtlich und ich spielte nur mit, weil mir "
"keine andere Wahl blieb."

#: meliss01.tra:420
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Well, your plan didn't work out quite like you thought.  Balthazar is still "
#| "alive."
msgid ""
"Well, your plan didn't work out quite like you thought. Balthazar is still "
"alive."
msgstr ""
"Nun, Euer Plan hat leider nicht wie vorgesehen funktioniert. Balthasar ist "
"immer noch am Leben."

#: meliss01.tra:422
#, fuzzy
#| msgctxt "MELISS23"
#| msgid ""
#| "Do you dare come and face me there?  Or shall I have to hunt you down like "
#| "the sorry dog that you are?  Because make no mistake... one way or another, "
#| "every last drop of that divine essence will be *mine*."
msgctxt "MELISS23"
msgid ""
"Do you dare come and face me there? Or shall I have to hunt you down like "
"the sorry dog that you are? Because make no mistake... one way or another, "
"every last drop of that divine essence will be *mine*."
msgstr ""
"Wagt Ihr es, dorthin zu kommen, und mir dort gegenüber zu treten?  Oder soll"
" ich Euch wie einen räudigen Hund jagen und zur Strecke bringen?  Wie dem "
"auch sein, auch der letzte Rest der göttlichen Essenz wird schließlich "
"*Mein* sein."

#: meliss01.tra:433
msgid ""
"As long as you did what you were required to and kill the Five, then I care "
"little for what you think you know, fool."
msgstr ""
"Solange Ihr tatet, was ich wollte, und gegen die Fünf kämpftet, war mir "
"völlig egal, was Ihr glaubtet zu wissen, Ihr Narr."

#: meliss01.tra:434
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "So you managed to corral Balthazar into co-operating with you?  I'm "
#| "surprised.  In the end, however, the essence of one or two of Bhaal's get "
#| "means very little."
msgid ""
"So you managed to corral Balthazar into co-operating with you? I'm "
"surprised. In the end, however, the essence of one or two of Bhaal's get "
"means very little."
msgstr ""
"So habt Ihr es also geschafft, Balthasar zu einer Kooperation zu überreden."
"  Ich bin überrascht.  Schließlich aber kommt es auf die Essenzen von ein "
"oder zwei Bhaalkindern nicht an."

#: player1.tra:314
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Slayer Ability Changed\n"
#| "\n"
#| "It appears my ability to control the transformation to the slayer has increased.  The slayer form itself is stronger, deadlier... and I am able to maintain it for longer.  The chances of going berserk while in the form have also decreased."
msgid ""
"Slayer Ability Changed\n"
"\n"
"It appears my ability to control the transformation to the slayer has increased. The slayer form itself is stronger, deadlier... and I am able to maintain it for longer. The chances of going berserk while in the form have also decreased."
msgstr ""
"Verwandlung in den Schlächter hat sich geändert\n"
"\n"
"Es scheint, dass meine Möglichkeiten, die Verwandlung in den Schlächter zu kontrollieren, sich verbessert haben.  Die Schlächterform ist stärker, tödlicher... und ich kann sie länger aufrecht erhalten.  Die Chancen, in einen unkontrollierbaren Berserkerrausch zu verfallen, haben sich ebenfalls verringert."

#: player1.tra:315
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Slayer Ability Changed Again\n"
#| "\n"
#| "My control over the slayer transformation continues to increase.  The slayer has become incredibly immune to harm and most magics, and it appears it is now immune to most diseases, poisons as well as any slow or hasting effects.  Even the slayer's claws now sometimes rip through magical effects and defenses."
msgid ""
"Slayer Ability Changed Again\n"
"\n"
"My control over the slayer transformation continues to increase. The slayer has become incredibly immune to harm and most magics, and it appears it is now immune to most diseases, poisons as well as any slow or hasting effects. Even the slayer's claws now sometimes rip through magical effects and defenses."
msgstr ""
"Verwandlung in den Schlächter hat sich erneut geändert\n"
"\n"
"Meine Kontrolle über die Verwandlung in den Schlächter wächst weiter.  Der Schlächter ist unglaublich immun gegen Schaden und die meiste Magie, und es scheint, dass er ebenso immun gegen Krankheit, Vergiftung sowie gegen alle Verlangsamungs- oder Beschleunigungseffekte ist.  Auch scheinen die Klauen des Schlächters manchmal durch Verteidigungszauber hindurch zu schlagen."

#: player1.tra:316
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "The Ravager Form\n"
#| "\n"
#| "I am not sure if this is a good thing or not... but my ability to control my transformation has progressed to the point where I can now become the ravager... optionally.  Although incredibly powerful... the ravager receives half damage from most attacks, is immune to any kind of immobilization or buffeting attack... the ravager is difficult for me to control and may be a danger to those nearby."
msgid ""
"The Ravager Form\n"
"\n"
"I am not sure if this is a good thing or not... but my ability to control my transformation has progressed to the point where I can now become the ravager... optionally. Although incredibly powerful... the ravager receives half damage from most attacks, is immune to any kind of immobilization or buffeting attack... the ravager is difficult for me to control and may be a danger to those nearby."
msgstr ""
"Verwandlung in den Wüter\n"
"\n"
"Ich bin mir nicht sicher, ob es eine gute Sache ist oder nicht... aber die Fähigkeiten, meine Verwandlung zu kontrollieren, haben einen Punkt erreicht, wo ich der Wüter werden kann... wenn ich will.  Obwohl unglaublich mächtig... der Wüter erhält nur den halben Schaden der meisten Angriffe, ist immun gegen jegliche Art von Festhalten oder Betäubung... ist der Wüter doch schwierig zu kontrollieren für mich und eine mögliche Gefahr für diejenigen, die mit mir sind."

#: player1.tra:317
msgid "I choose to turn into the ravager."
msgstr "Ich will mich in den Wüter verwandeln."

#: player1.tra:396
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "With the initial battle now over, you consider your options.  In the stream "
#| "of energy within the center of the Throne, Melissan appears to be "
#| "invulnerable to harm... and growing in power every second.  She must be "
#| "drawn out willingly in order to defeat her."
msgid ""
"With the initial battle now over, you consider your options. In the stream "
"of energy within the center of the Throne, Melissan appears to be "
"invulnerable to harm... and growing in power every second. She must be drawn"
" out willingly in order to defeat her."
msgstr ""
"Nachdem der erste Kampf vorbei ist, überdenkt Ihr Eure Möglichkeiten. Im "
"Energiestrom in der Mitte des Throns scheint Melissan unverwundbar zu "
"sein... und ihre Macht mit jedem Augenblick zu wachsen.  Ihr müsst sie dazu "
"bringen, freiwillig heraus zu kommen, damit Ihr sie besiegen könnt."

#: player1.tra:397
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "The only option you can think of seem to be regarding the three 'essence "
#| "pools' that adjoin the Throne.  Your own link to the essence might allow you"
#| " to cut off the flow of energy to Melissan from these pools, forcing her to "
#| "fight.  The pools are, however, likely to be guarded..."
msgid ""
"The only option you can think of seem to be regarding the three 'essence "
"pools' that adjoin the Throne. Your own link to the essence might allow you "
"to cut off the flow of energy to Melissan from these pools, forcing her to "
"fight. The pools are, however, likely to be guarded..."
msgstr ""
"Die einzige Möglichkeit, die Euch einfällt, scheint mit den drei "
"\"Essenzbecken\" zusammenzuhängen, die sich in der Nähe des Throns befinden."
"  Eure eigene Verbindung zur Essenz könnte es Euch erlauben, den Fluss der "
"Energie von diesen Becken zu Melissan zu unterbrechen und sie damit zum "
"Kampf zu zwingen.  Die Becken werden allerdings wohl bewacht..."

#: player1.tra:398
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Melissan continues to restore her divine energies at the fountain, keeping "
#| "her immortality intact.  There must be a way to weaken her further, or you "
#| "will never be able to defeat her."
msgid ""
"Melissan continues to restore her divine energies at the fountain, keeping "
"her immortality intact. There must be a way to weaken her further, or you "
"will never be able to defeat her."
msgstr ""
"Melissan stellt ihre göttlichen Energien an der Quelle wieder her und "
"bewahrt so ihre Unsterblichkeit.  Ihr müsst einen Weg finden, sie noch mehr "
"zu schwächen, oder Ihr werdet sie nie besiegen können."

#: ppguy02.tra:1
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You interpose your hand in the swirl of energy within the pool, but its "
#| "power is obviously too much for you.  You do not interrupt its flow and, "
#| "instead, the energy leaps out and damages you."
msgid ""
"You interpose your hand in the swirl of energy within the pool, but its "
"power is obviously too much for you. You do not interrupt its flow and, "
"instead, the energy leaps out and damages you."
msgstr ""
"Ihr haltet Eure Hand in die wirbelnde Energie des Pools, aber dessen Macht "
"ist offensichtlich zu stark für Euch.  Ihr könnt den Fluss nicht "
"unterbrechen, und stattdessen springt Energie heraus und verletzt Euch."

#: ppguy02.tra:2
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You place your hand within the energies of the pool and draw the essence "
#| "into yourself, diverting it away from Melissan.  Boundless power fills you "
#| "briefly, and while most of it dissipates a portion fuels your inner "
#| "energies.  You are now immune to death magics and vorpal effects, and have "
#| "also gained the ability to unleash the power within you as a short burst of "
#| "destructive power.  The energies also restore the powers of all present."
msgid ""
"You place your hand within the energies of the pool and draw the essence "
"into yourself, diverting it away from Melissan. Boundless power fills you "
"briefly, and while most of it dissipates a portion fuels your inner "
"energies. You are now immune to death magics and vorpal effects, and have "
"also gained the ability to unleash the power within you as a short burst of "
"destructive power. The energies also restore the powers of all present."
msgstr ""
"Ihr haltet Eure Hand in die Energie des Beckens, zieht die Essenz in Euch "
"selbst hinein und lenkt sie so von Melissan ab.  Für einen Moment seid Ihr "
"von grenzenloser Macht erfüllt... und obwohl der größte Teil Euch wieder "
"verlässt und sich im Raum zerstreut, füllt ein Teil davon Eure inneren "
"Energien.  Ihr seid nun immun gegenüber Todesmagie und Sofortigem Tod und "
"besitzt die Fähigkeit, die Macht in Euch in einem kurzen Ausbruch "
"zerstörerischer Kraft zu entfesseln.  Die Energien stellen außerdem die "
"Kräfte aller Anwesenden wieder her."

#: ppguy02.tra:3 ppguy02.tra:4
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "New power gained: \"Unleash\"\n"
#| "\n"
#| "The \"Unleash\" ability releases your inner power upon a target that is within melee range, hitting them for 10d12 magic damage (half on a successful save vs. Death) and sending them flying back and perhaps unconscious for a short period.  This ability may only be used once ever thirty seconds... and after using it the Bhaalspawn will be incredibly fatigued and have a 25% miscast chance on all spells for 2 rounds.  Due to the amount of divine essence used, the Slayer form will also not be available for thirty seconds."
msgid ""
"New power gained: \"Unleash\"\n"
"\n"
"The \"Unleash\" ability releases your inner power upon a target that is within melee range, hitting them for 10d12 magic damage (half on a successful save vs. Death) and sending them flying back and perhaps unconscious for a short period. This ability may only be used once ever thirty seconds... and after using it the Bhaalspawn will be incredibly fatigued and have a 25% miscast chance on all spells for 2 rounds. Due to the amount of divine essence used, the Slayer form will also not be available for thirty seconds."
msgstr ""
"Neue Fähigkeit erhalten: \"Entfesseln\"\n"
"\n"
"Die Fähigkeit \"Entfesseln\" setzt Eure innere Kraft frei und trifft ein Ziel in Nahkampfreichweite, wobei 10W10 Schadenspunkte verursacht werden (ein erfolgreicher Rettungswurf gegen Zauber halbiert den Schaden) und das Opfer zurückgestoßen und möglicherweise für eine kurze Zeit bewusstlos wird.  Diese Fähigkeit kann einmal je 30 Sekunden eingesetzt werden... und danach ist das Bhaalkind sehr stark ermüdet und erleidet für 2 Runden eine 25%ige Chance, dass Zauber fehlschlagen.  Aufgrund der verbrauchten Menge an göttlicher Essenz steht Euch auch die Verwandlung in den Schlächter 30 Sekunden lang nicht zur Verfügung."

#: ppguy02.tra:5
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You place your hand within the energies of the pool and draw the essence "
#| "into yourself, diverting it away from Melissan.  Boundless power fills you, "
#| "and while most of it dissipates you are left with much of Bhaal's essence.  "
#| "For the moment, you have gained the ability to teleport freely throughout "
#| "space and also fight for control of abyssal demons that are under Melissan's"
#| " control. Part of this ability to teleport also means you are now completely"
#| " immune to the spells Maze and Imprisonment.  The energies also restore the "
#| "powers of all present."
msgid ""
"You place your hand within the energies of the pool and draw the essence "
"into yourself, diverting it away from Melissan. Boundless power fills you, "
"and while most of it dissipates you are left with much of Bhaal's essence. "
"For the moment, you have gained the ability to teleport freely throughout "
"space and also fight for control of abyssal demons that are under Melissan's"
" control. Part of this ability to teleport also means you are now completely"
" immune to the spells Maze and Imprisonment. The energies also restore the "
"powers of all present."
msgstr ""
"Ihr haltet Eure Hand in die Energie des Beckens, zieht die Essenz in Euch "
"selbst hinein und lenkt sie so von Melissan ab.  Für einen Moment seid Ihr "
"von grenzenloser Macht erfüllt... und obwohl der größte Teil Euch wieder "
"verlässt und sich im Raum zerstreut, bleibt doch viel von Bhaals Essenz in "
"Euch.  Ihr habt die Fähigkeit erhalten, Euch frei durch den Raum zu "
"teleportieren und zudem um die Kontrolle über die Dämonen der Abyss zu "
"kämpfen, die jetzt unter Melissans Kontrolle stehen.  Als Nebenwirkung Eurer"
" Fähigkeit der Teleportation seid Ihr nun auch vollständig immun gegenüber "
"den Zaubern Irrgarten und Einkerkerung.  Die Energien stellen außerdem die "
"Kräfte aller Anwesenden wieder her."

#: ppguy02.tra:6
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "New power gained: \"Control Demon\"\n"
#| "\n"
#| "This ability allows the Bhaalspawn to attempt to wrest control of a demon away from Melissan and make them an ally.  The Bhaalspawn engages the demon in mental combat for 1 round, at the end of which the demon has a chance of becoming an ally.  The demon is not under the Bhaalspawn's direct control, however.  This ability may be used once every 3 rounds.\n"
#| "\n"
#| "New power gained: \"Dimension Door\"\n"
#| "\n"
#| "The Bhaalspawn may now move freely through space and the planes.  This teleportation power is useable once per round."
msgid ""
"New power gained: \"Control Demon\"\n"
"\n"
"This ability allows the Bhaalspawn to attempt to wrest control of a demon away from Melissan and make them an ally. The Bhaalspawn engages the demon in mental combat for 1 round, at the end of which the demon has a chance of becoming an ally. The demon is not under the Bhaalspawn's direct control, however. This ability may be used once every 3 rounds.\n"
"\n"
"New power gained: \"Dimension Door\"\n"
"\n"
"The Bhaalspawn may now move freely through space and the planes. This teleportation power is useable once per round."
msgstr ""
"Neue Fähigkeit erhalten: \"Dämon beherrschen\"\n"
"\n"
"Diese Fähigkeit erlaubt es dem Bhaalkind zu versuchen, die Herrschaft über einen Dämon von Melissan zu erringen und ihn zu einem Verbündeten zu machen.  Das Bhaalkind kämpft für 1 Runde mit dem Dämon um geistige Herrschaft, und am Ende der Runde besteht die Möglichkeit, dass der Dämon Euer Verbündeter wird.  Er ist jedoch nicht unter Eurer direkten Kontrolle.  Die Fähigkeit kann einmal je 3 Runden eingesetzt werden.\n"
"\n"
"Neue Fähigkeit erhalten: \"Dimensionstor\"\n"
"\n"
"Das Bhaalkind kann sich nun frei durch den Raum und die Ebenen bewegen.  Diese Fähigkeit der Teleportation kann einmal pro Runde eingesetzt werden."

#: ppguy02.tra:7
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You place your hand within the energies of the pool and draw the essence "
#| "into yourself, diverting it away from Melissan.  You are filled with "
#| "boundless power for a moment... and while most of it leaves you and "
#| "dissipates into the cosmos, a part of it remains with you.  You have gained "
#| "the ability to focus the energies within you to protect yourself from such "
#| "magics as Time Stop, Disintegrate and Flesh to Stone for a short period.  "
#| "The energies also restore the powers of all present."
msgid ""
"You place your hand within the energies of the pool and draw the essence "
"into yourself, diverting it away from Melissan. You are filled with "
"boundless power for a moment... and while most of it leaves you and "
"dissipates into the cosmos, a part of it remains with you. You have gained "
"the ability to focus the energies within you to protect yourself from such "
"magics as Time Stop, Disintegrate and Flesh to Stone for a short period. The"
" energies also restore the powers of all present."
msgstr ""
"Ihr haltet Eure Hand in die Energie des Beckens, zieht die Essenz in Euch "
"selbst hinein und lenkt sie so von Melissan ab.  Für einen Moment seid Ihr "
"von grenzenloser Macht erfüllt... und obwohl der größte Teil Euch wieder "
"verlässt und sich im Raum zerstreut, bleibt ein Teil davon in Euch.  Ihr "
"habt die Fähigkeit erhalten, die Energien in Euch zu fokussieren, um Euch "
"vor Magie wie Zeitstop, Auflösung und Versteinerung für eine kurze Zeit zu "
"schützen.  Die Energien stellen außerdem die Kräfte aller Anwesenden wieder "
"her."

#: ppguy02.tra:9
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "New power gained: \"Focus\"\n"
#| "\n"
#| "This ability allows the Bhaalspawn to focus his energy within him to resist spell effects from without.  For a 30-second duration, the Bhaalspawn becomes immune to the spells Flesh to Stone, Disintegration and Time Stop.  All minor spells of 1st through 3rd level will also not affect the Bhaalspawn.  This ability is useable once per minute."
msgid ""
"New power gained: \"Focus\"\n"
"\n"
"This ability allows the Bhaalspawn to focus his energy within him to resist spell effects from without. For a 30-second duration, the Bhaalspawn becomes immune to the spells Flesh to Stone, Disintegration and Time Stop. All minor spells of 1st through 3rd level will also not affect the Bhaalspawn. This ability is useable once per minute."
msgstr ""
"Neue Fähigkeit erhalten: \"Fokus\"\n"
"\n"
"Diese Fähigkeit erlaubt es dem Bhaalkind, die inneren Energien zu fokussieren, um äußeren Zauberwirkungen zu widerstehen.  Für eine Dauer von 30 Sekunden wird das Bhaalkind immun gegen die Zauber Fleisch zu Stein, Auflösung und Zeitstop.  Auch alle Zauber der Grade 1 bis 3 haben keine Auswirkungen.  Diese Fähigkeit kann einmal pro Minute angewendet werden."

#: ppguy02.tra:10
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "The final pool has been stilled.  The light of the energy column has begun "
#| "to ebb.  You have only moments to prepare for what is surely the final "
#| "confrontation..."
msgid ""
"The final pool has been stilled. The light of the energy column has begun to"
" ebb. You have only moments to prepare for what is surely the final "
"confrontation..."
msgstr ""
"Das letzte Becken ist stillgelegt.  Das Licht der Energiesäule wird "
"schwächer.  Ihr habt nur wenige Augenblicke, um Euch auf den Kampf "
"vorzubereiten, der mit Sicherheit die letzte Konfrontation sein wird..."

#: ppguy02.tra:11
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Already Melissan begins to stir within the stream of divine energies.  Once "
#| "the last pool is stilled, there will be very little time before she reacts."
msgid ""
"Already Melissan begins to stir within the stream of divine energies. Once "
"the last pool is stilled, there will be very little time before she reacts."
msgstr ""
"Schon beginnt Melissan, sich innerhalb des Stroms göttlicher Energien zu "
"rühren.  Sobald das letzte Becken stillgelegt ist, wird Euch nur sehr wenig "
"Zeit bleiben, bevor sie reagiert."

#: sarev25j.tra:262
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "What do you mean, wench?  We've no business, you and I."
msgid "What do you mean, wench? We've no business, you and I."
msgstr ""
"Was meint Ihr, Weib?  Wir haben nichts miteinander zu tun, Ihr und ich."

#: sarev25j.tra:263
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Even if cared to consider your offer, I cannot.  <CHARNAME> has bound me "
#| "with a vow."
msgid ""
"Even if cared to consider your offer, I cannot. <CHARNAME> has bound me with"
" a vow."
msgstr ""
"Auch wenn ich über Euer Angebot nachdenken wollte, so kann ich es doch "
"nicht.  <CHARNAME> hat mich mit einem Schwur gebunden."

#: sarev25j.tra:264
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I see.  And you believe your offer interests me?  <CHARNAME> has done well "
#| "enough against you so far."
msgid ""
"I see. And you believe your offer interests me? <CHARNAME> has done well "
"enough against you so far."
msgstr ""
"Ich sehe es.  Und Ihr glaubt, Euer Angebot interessiere mich?  <CHARNAME> "
"hat sich gut genug gegen Euch gehalten."

#: sarev25j.tra:265
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Serve you?  You made me that offer once, as I recall.  I strung up your "
#| "messenger atop the spires of my tower and allowed the crows to feed upon his"
#| " innards.  I desired to rule, not to serve.  And I will not serve you, "
#| "wench.  My answer is no."
msgid ""
"Serve you? You made me that offer once, as I recall. I strung up your "
"messenger atop the spires of my tower and allowed the crows to feed upon his"
" innards. I desired to rule, not to serve. And I will not serve you, wench. "
"My answer is no."
msgstr ""
"Euch dienen?  Ihr machtet mir dieses Angebot schon einmal, wenn ich mich "
"recht entsinne.  Ich hängte Euren Boten an der Spitze meines Turmes auf und "
"erlaubte den Krähen, seine Eingeweide zu fressen.  Ich will herrschen, nicht"
" dienen.  Und schon gar nicht werde ich Euch dienen, Weib.  Meine Antwort "
"ist Nein."

#: sarev25j.tra:266
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I tire of <CHARNAME> and <PRO_HISHER> foolish morals.  I tire of tagging "
#| "along as a servant to the one who halted my own plans long before yours came"
#| " to fruition, priestess.  Aye... I will be your general."
msgid ""
"I tire of <CHARNAME> and <PRO_HISHER> foolish morals. I tire of tagging "
"along as a servant to the one who halted my own plans long before yours came"
" to fruition, priestess. Aye... I will be your general."
msgstr ""
"Ich habe <CHARNAME> und <PRO_HISHER>e törichte Moral satt.  Ich habe es "
"satt, demjenigen als Diener hinterher zu trotten, der meine Pläne zunichte "
"machte, lange bevor Eure sich verwirklichten, Priesterin.  Ja... ich werde "
"Euer General sein."

#: sarev25j.tra:267
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "No, Sarevok!  You traitorous bastard!"
msgid "No, Sarevok! You traitorous bastard!"
msgstr "Nein, Sarevok!  Ihr treuloser Bastard!"

#: sarev25j.tra:268
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "That is a mistake, Sarevok.  You'll just die along with her this way."
msgid "That is a mistake, Sarevok. You'll just die along with her this way."
msgstr ""
"Das ist ein Fehler, Sarevok.  Auf diese Weise werdet Ihr mit ihr sterben."

#: sarev25j.tra:269
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I expected as much.  So I get to kill you again, as well.  It's all good."
msgid ""
"I expected as much. So I get to kill you again, as well. It's all good."
msgstr ""
"Wie ich es erwartet habe.  Und so muß ich Euch eben ein weiteres Mal töten."
"  Auch gut."

#: sarev25j.tra:270
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Become the demon I once was?  I am no longer that man, nor do I wish to be."
#| "  If <CHARNAME> has shown me anything, it is that I am better off untouched "
#| "by the madness that once swallowed me whole.  Wallow in your delusion if you"
#| " will, woman... I remember it well.  And I will not join you in it."
msgid ""
"Become the demon I once was? I am no longer that man, nor do I wish to be. "
"If <CHARNAME> has shown me anything, it is that I am better off untouched by"
" the madness that once swallowed me whole. Wallow in your delusion if you "
"will, woman... I remember it well. And I will not join you in it."
msgstr ""
"Der Dämon sein, der ich einst war?  Ich bin nicht länger dieser Mann und ich"
" wünsche es auch nicht wieder zu sein.  Wenn <CHARNAME> mir eins gezeigt "
"hat, dann dass ich besser dran bin ohne den Wahnsinn, der einst völlig von "
"mir Besitz ergriffen hatte.  Schwelgt in Euren Wahnvorstellungen, Weib... "
"ich erinnere mich noch gut.  Und ich werde Euch nicht dorthin folgen."

#: sarev25j.tra:271
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "My nature has not changed, <CHARNAME>.  Did you truly expect otherwise?  "
#| "Better to fight for Melissan than sit in your shadow and watch you take what"
#| " was once mine."
msgid ""
"My nature has not changed, <CHARNAME>. Did you truly expect otherwise? "
"Better to fight for Melissan than sit in your shadow and watch you take what"
" was once mine."
msgstr ""
"Meine Natur hat sich nicht geändert, <CHARNAME>.  Habt Ihr das wirklich "
"erwartet?  Es ist besser für Melissan zu kämpfen als in Eurem Schatten zu "
"sitzen und zu sehen, wie Ihr nehmt, was einst mir gehörte."

#: sarev25j.tra:272
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Perhaps.  But I will not sit in your shadow and simply watch you take what "
#| "was once mine.  You do not deserve power, <CHARNAME>.  Even if it means "
#| "fighting for Melissan, I will do what I must."
msgid ""
"Perhaps. But I will not sit in your shadow and simply watch you take what "
"was once mine. You do not deserve power, <CHARNAME>. Even if it means "
"fighting for Melissan, I will do what I must."
msgstr ""
"Vielleicht.  Aber ich werde nicht in Eurem Schatten sitzen und zusehen, wie "
"Ihr nehmt, was einst mir gehörte.  Ihr verdient diese Macht nicht, "
"<CHARNAME>.  Selbst wenn es bedeutet für Melissan zu kämpfen.  Ich tue, was "
"ich tun muss."

#: sarev25j.tra:273
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "A typical boast.  And perhaps you will even win, but I will not sit idly by "
#| "as you take what was once mine.  You don't deserve power, <CHARNAME>, and "
#| "even if it means fighting for Melissan I will do what I must."
msgid ""
"A typical boast. And perhaps you will even win, but I will not sit idly by "
"as you take what was once mine. You don't deserve power, <CHARNAME>, and "
"even if it means fighting for Melissan I will do what I must."
msgstr ""
"Eure typische Prahlerei.  Und vielleicht werdet Ihr sogar gewinnen, aber ich"
" werde nicht ruhig zusehen, wie Ihr nehmt, was einst mir gehörte.  Ihr "
"verdient diese Macht nicht, <CHARNAME>, und selbst wenn es bedeutet, für "
"Melissan zu kämpfen, so werde ich tun, was ich tun muss."

#: sarev25j.tra:274
