#| "yourself, god-child.  You are to be commended.  Your journey is nearly at "
#| "its end."
msgid ""
"You have parleyed with Balthazar, the greatest of the Bhaalspawn besides "
"yourself, god-child. You are to be commended. Your journey is nearly at its "
"end."
msgstr ""
"Ihr habt Euch mit Balthasar, dem neben Euch mächtigsten der Bhaalkinder, "
"verbündet. Ein weiterer Schritt ist getan und Eure Reise ist beinahe an "
"ihrem Ende angelangt."

