#: solar.tra:243
msgid ""
"So Melissan has not collected enough of the essence, yet, to resurrect "
"Bhaal, right?"
msgstr ""
"Also hat Melissan noch nicht genug Essenzen gesammelt, um Bhaal wieder "
"auferstehen zu lassen, nicht wahr?"

