msgid ""
"So, Melissan seeks to be the last of the Bhaalspawn. Does she even plan on "
"resurrecting Bhaal?"
msgstr ""
"So versucht Melissan also das letzte der Bhaalkinder zu sein. Plant auch sie"
" die Wiederauferstehung Bhaals?"

